%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20History%20Congress%20Opposes%20Demolition%20of%20National%20Museum%20Building%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05123902%2F2268292509_c6a540e595_b.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Indian%20History%20Congress%20(IHC)%2C%20which%20recently%20held%20its%20annual%20conclave%20in%20Kakatiya%20University%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20unanimously%20opposed%20the%20proposed%20demolition%20of%20the%20building%20that%20houses%20the%20National%20Museum%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Central%20Vista%20project%20and%20expressed%20its%20concern%20over%20the%20shifting%20of%20over%202%2C00%2C000%20artefacts%20containing%20%E2%80%9Cthousands%20of%20years%20of%20cultural%20heritage%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20resolution%20passed%20by%20the%20IHC%20said%20that%20the%20National%20Museum%20will%20be%20eventually%20shifted%20to%20the%20proposed%20Yuge%20Yugeen%20Bharat%20National%20Museum%20in%20the%20North%20Block%20and%20South%20Block%20of%20the%20Raisina%20Hill%20complex%2C%20originally%20planned%20as%20new%20office%20buildings.%20While%20it%20said%20that%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20office%20premises%20will%20be%20highly%20unsuitable%20to%20accommodate%20a%20museum%2C%20it%20added%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20move%20seems%20to%20be%20an%20attempt%20towards%20making%20a%20more%20controlled%20and%20less%20accessible%20National%20Museum%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20impedes%20easy%20public%20accessibility%20and%20directly%20contradicts%20the%20vision%20that%20the%20National%20Museum%20had%20envisaged%20in%20the%20early%20years%20after%20our%20Independence.%20Thus%2C%20the%20core%20idea%20of%20dissemination%20of%20knowledge%20related%20to%20history%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20artistic%20excellence%20gets%20sabotaged%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20resolution%20said.%20It%20further%20expressed%20its%20concern%20over%20the%20non-transparency%20over%20the%20process%20of%20transfer%20of%20the%20artefacts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6till%20the%20new%20Museum%20space%20is%20ready%2C%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20collection%20of%20the%20National%20Museum%20hangs%20by%20a%20thread%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMonuments%20represent%20the%20vision%20and%20authority%20of%20those%20in%20power.%20The%20shifting%20of%20the%20National%20Museum%20from%20its%20current%20location%20to%20incorporate%20the%20Central%20Vista%20project%20is%20a%20symbol%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20change%20the%20basic%20ethos%20and%20fabric%20of%20the%20Indian%20political%20system.%20The%20Indian%20History%20Congress%20strongly%20condemns%20the%20constant%20disregard%20of%20historical%20artefacts%20and%20the%20move%20to%20shift%20the%20National%20Museum%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20IHC%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtection%20of%20Indian%20monuments%20figured%20among%20the%20most%20important%20concerns%20of%20the%20IHC.%20It%20passed%20two%20other%20resolutions%20that%20called%20on%20the%20government%20to%20take%20extra%20caution%20in%20dealing%20with%20monuments%20that%20are%20being%20targeted%20by%20vested%20political%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20buildings%2C%20whatever%20their%20nature%2C%20if%20over%20200%20years%20old%2C%20should%20be%20strictly%20protected%2C%20under%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20Protection%20of%20Monuments%20Act%2C%20and%20their%20character%2C%20if%20these%20are%20religious%20structures%2C%20should%20not%20be%20altered%3B%20and%2C%20where%20worship%20has%20ceased%2C%20it%20should%20not%20be%20restored.%20It%20feels%20that%20this%20is%20also%20the%20obligation%20imposed%20on%20the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20by%20the%20Protection%20of%20Monuments%20Act%2C%20and%20other%20existing%20legislation%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%20of%20the%20IHC%E2%80%99s%20resolutions%20said%20in%20the%20context%20of%20judicial%20proceedings%20in%20the%20matters%20concerning%20the%20Shahi%20Idgah%20in%20Mathura%20and%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20in%20Varanasi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20resolution%20strongly%20condemned%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20recent%20attempt%20to%20remove%20the%20Sunheri%20Masjid%2C%20a%20Mughal-era%20monument%20which%20even%20the%20Britishers%20had%20left%20untouched%20during%20the%20construction%20of%20Delhi%20as%20the%20imperial%20capital%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20IHC%20said%20that%20while%20such%20political%20calls%20to%20alter%20the%20nature%20of%20historical%20monuments%20are%20being%20made%2C%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cdisturbing%E2%80%9D%20to%20see%20the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20has%20%E2%80%9Cabandoned%20its%20project%20of%20annual%20reports%20and%20regular%20publication%20of%20the%20journal%20%3Cem%3EAncient%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20as%20also%20its%20two%20epigraphic%20journals%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20vitally%20important%20that%20all%20of%20these%20be%20revived%2C%20properly%20edited%20and%20regularly%20published%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20IHC%20said%20in%20one%20of%20its%20six%20resolutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%201935-36%20in%20Allahabad%2C%20the%20IHC%20is%20the%20largest%20body%20in%20India%20comprising%20professional%20historians%20and%20has%20advocated%20for%20a%20scientific%20and%20fact-based%20approach%20towards%20historical%20research%20and%20played%20a%20dominant%20role%20in%20opposing%20%E2%80%9Cmythification%E2%80%9D%20of%20history.%20The%2082nd%20IHC%20conclave%20happened%20between%20December%2028-30%2C%202023%2C%20during%20which%201%2C070%20research%20papers%20were%20presented%20by%20historians.%20This%20is%20the%20second%20time%20the%20IHC%20session%20was%20conducted%20in%20Warangal%E2%80%99s%20Kakatiya%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20session%20also%20saw%20Professor%20Aditya%20Mukherjee%20taking%20charge%20as%20the%20newly-elected%20general%20president%20of%20the%20IHC%20from%20the%20outgoing%20president%20Professor%20Kesavan%20Veluthat.%20During%20the%20session%2C%20historian%20and%20columnist%20Ramachandra%20Guha%20was%20also%20chosen%20for%20the%20Lifetime%20Achievement%20Award%2C%20given%20every%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20resolutions%2C%20the%20IHC%20reiterated%20its%20previous%20criticisms%20on%20how%20History%20Syllabi%20is%20being%20tampered%20with%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20implementing%20the%20%E2%80%9CNational%20Educational%20Policy%E2%80%9D.%20The%20IHC%20said%20that%20the%20history%20books%20were%20being%20altered%20%E2%80%9Cfor%20presenting%20a%20very%20coloured%20and%20inaccurate%20vision%20of%20Indian%20history%20in%20our%20schools%2C%20colleges%20and%20universities%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20manifest%20in%20the%20official%20decree%20to%20make%20compulsory%20the%20study%20of%20%E2%80%9CIndian%20knowledge%20system%E2%80%9D%2C%20of%20which%20caste-ridden%20ancient%20texts%20are%20cited%20as%20examples%2C%20along%20with%20a%20curiously%20entrenched%20concern%20with%20the%20Aryan%20race.%20This%20is%20accompanied%20by%20overlooking%20much%20of%20our%20social%2C%20economic%2C%20intellectual%20and%20art%20history%2C%20and%20in%20picturing%20the%20medieval%20period%20as%20a%20time%20when%20India%20was%20under%20foreign%20thraldom%2C%20etc.%20Even%20Akbar%20is%20excluded%20from%20the%20detailed%20Indian%20History%20syllabus%20for%20the%20Bachelor%20programme%20framed%20by%20the%20University%20Grants%20Commission.%20Needless%20to%20say%2C%20little%20or%20no%20concern%20is%20shown%20for%20fields%20such%20as%20economic%20history%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20history%2C%20or%20the%20history%20of%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20IHC%20resolution%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IHC%20also%20called%20for%20an%20%E2%80%9Cimmediate%20ceasefire%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20conflict%20and%20%E2%80%9Can%20end%20to%20displacement%20of%20the%20hapless%20Palestinians%20from%20their%20homeland%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A17054