20ever%20known.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-generation-alpha-how-shop-spend-education-work-live-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705402621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a18e4a6979d7371822f773%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-generation-alpha-how-shop-spend-education-work-live-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Generation%20Alpha%20might%20be%20swarming%20Sephoras%20right%20now%2C%20but%20they'll%20be%20an%20economic%20force%20to%20be%20reckoned%20with.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Juliana%20Kaplan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-generation-alpha-how-shop-spend-education-work-live-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22You%20don't%20need%20to%20buy%20a%20%248%20Blue%20Zone%20frozen%20meal.%20Here's%20how%20to%20make%20your%20own%20for%20under%20%242%20a%20serving.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221804%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20split%20image%20showing%20a%20Blue%20Zones%20frozen%20meal%20and%20a%20hungry%20reporter%20wishing%20there%20was%20a%20larger%20serving%20of%20food.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a1b7a16979d7371823191f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHow%20it%20started%20vs.%20how%20it%20went%20%E2%80%94%20this%20was%20delicious%20but%20just%20not%20enough%20food%20for%20a%20whole%20meal%3Cp%3EGabby%20Landsverk%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBlue%20Zones%20Kitchen%20bowls%20aim%20to%20bring%20healthy%20food%20to%20the%20freezer%20aisle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20taste%20great%20%E2%80%93%20but%20for%20up%20to%20%248%20a%20bowl%20it's%20hard%20not%20to%20feel%20like%20we%20could%20make%20this%20cheaper%20at%20home.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETo%20make%20your%20own%20bowls%2C%20grab%20a%20slow%20cooker%2C%20some%20citrus%2C%20and%20a%20few%20cans%20of%20beans%20to%20start.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20favorite%20food%20is%20free%20food%2C%20and%20as%20a%20nutrition%20writer%2C%20anything%20healthy%20I%20can%20get%20is%20icing%20on%20the%20cake%20(so%20to%20speak).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20couldn't%20wait%20to%20dig%20into%20some%20complimentary%20frozen%20test%20meals%20based%20on%20some%20of%20the%20longest-living%20(and%20most%20culinarily%20gifted)%20regions%20of%20the%20world%20known%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblue-zone-residents-longevity-secrets-traits-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBlue%20Zones%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20places%20like%20Italy%2C%20Greece%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20Costa%20Rica.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20snarfed%20down%20the%20tangy%2C%20citrus-forward%20Okinawa-inspired%20sesame%20ginger%20bowl%20at%20noon%20on%20a%20wintery%20Friday%2C%20and%20I%20was%20not%20disappointed.%20This%20240-calorie%20bowl%20tasted%20almost%20as%20good%20as%20home%20cooking%2C%20was%20full%20of%20nutrients%2C%20and%20was%20ready%20in%20less%20than%20five%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20not%20even%20an%20hour%20later%2C%20my%20stomach%20was%20grumbling%20and%20I%20was%20raiding%20the%20freezer%20for%20another%20round.%20That's%20when%20I%20had%20second%20thoughts%20about%20eating%20these%20bowls%20on%20the%20regular.%20At%20about%20%246%20to%20%248%20per%20serving%2C%20they%20might%20help%20me%20extend%20my%20lifespan%20by%20eating%20more%20healthy%20veggies%20and%20grains%20more%20often%2C%20but%20they%20would%20deal%20a%20fatal%20blow%20to%20my%20already%20frail%20grocery%20budget%20while%20doing%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Blue%20Zones%20meals%20were%20tasty%20and%20convenient%20but%20left%20me%20hungry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22why%20so%20small%20sesame%20ginger%20bowl%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a19831dcdb354a985744c8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20is%20not%20enough%20lunch%20for%20me.%20It's%20roughly%20two%20to%20three%20handfuls%20of%20food.%20%3Cp%3EHilary%20Brueck%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessinsider.com%2Fblue-zone-frozen-meals-tasty-healthy-expensive-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEating%20the%20bean-filled%20bowls%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20great.%20Every%20bite%20was%20full%20of%20flavor%20and%20recognizable%20ingredients%2C%20without%20the%20typical%20ultra-processing%20of%20most%20convenience%20foods.%20These%20bowls%20were%20just%20variations%20on%20a%20theme%20of%20beans%2C%20vegetables%2C%20plus%20whole%20grains%20%E2%80%94%20no%20additives%2C%20extra%20sugar%2C%20or%20unpronounceable%20preservatives%20inside.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20problem%20is%20that%20the%20delicious%20experience%20was%20short-lived%20%E2%80%94%20within%20about%20eight%20bites%2C%20my%20odyssey%20to%20the%20world's%20fountains%20of%20youth%20had%20ended.%20Normally%2C%20my%20lunches%20are%20around%20600%20calories%2C%20often%20more.%20After%20this%20240-calorie%20bowl%2C%20I%20was%20still%20hungry.%20Do%20I%20grab%20a%20Hot%20Pocket%20now%2C%20or%20what%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ended%20up%20eating%20two%20packages%20to%20make%20a%20satisfying%20meal%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20this%20way.%20The%20nutritional%20profile%20of%20the%20meals%20is%20good%2C%20with%20lots%20of%20fiber%20and%20a%20decent%20amount%20of%20protein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223626%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22four%20boxes%20of%20Blue%20Zones%20frozen%20meals%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a1ba0b6979d73718231a30%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222719%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20is%20technically%20four%20meals%2C%20but%20truth%20be%20told%2C%20I%20could%20have%20easily%20eaten%20all%20of%20them%20on%20a%20particularly%20hungry%20day.%20%3Cp%3EGabby%20Landsverk%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20extra%20scoop%20or%20two%20of%20quinoa%2C%20edamame%2C%20or%20black%20beans%20would%20do%20it%2C%20really.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20exciting%20discoveries%20in%20Blue%20Zones%20research%20is%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F7-longevity-boosting-foods-blue-zones-add-to-shopping-list-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eingredients%20linked%20to%20longevity%20aren't%20expensive%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20exotic%2C%20or%20hard%20to%20prepare%2C%20and%20they%20are%20satiating%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20colleague%20Hilary%20Brueck%20largely%20agreed.%20While%20the%20310-calorie%20Heirloom%20Rice%20Bowl%20was%20enough%20of%20a%20lunch%20for%20her%2C%20the%20240-calorie%20Sesame%20Ginger%20Bowl%20was%20so%20small%20she%20was%20able%20to%20rush%20outside%20for%20a%20run%20shortly%20after%20eating%20it%2C%20which%20felt%20a%20little%20weird.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20really%20healthy%2C%20delicious%20snack!%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20edamame%20is%20crunchy%2C%20and%20the%20sauce%20is%20so%20creamy-gingery.%26quot%3B%20The%20yum%20factor%20rivaled%20the%20umami%20of%20meatier%2C%20fattier%20meals%20she's%20had%20%E2%80%94%20without%20any%20butter%20or%20animal%20products%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20easier%20than%20you%20might%20think%20to%20recreate%20the%20meals%20at%20home%20%E2%80%94%20and%20cheaper%2C%20too%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20have%20the%20impression%20that%20they%20don't%20have%20time%20to%20cook%2C%26quot%3B%20Blue%20Zones%20expert%20Dan%20Buettner%20told%20Business%20Insider%20over%20the%20phone%2C%20while%20admiring%20his%20own%20fr