22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGreg%20Schwartz%20pivoted%20from%20UX%20designer%20to%20prompt%20engineer%20on%20Upwork.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Greg%20Schwartz%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGreg%20Schwartz%20started%20as%20a%20freelance%20prompt%20engineer%20on%20Upwork%20in%20March%202023.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20shared%20how%20he%20works%20with%20clients%20to%20improve%20their%20prompts%20for%20AI%20chatbots%20like%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESchwartz%20said%20it's%20important%20to%20tell%20the%20chatbot%20what%20its%20role%20is%20and%20give%20it%20plenty%20of%20context.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20transcribed%20conversation%20with%20Greg%20Schwartz%20about%20working%20as%20a%20freelancer%20on%20Upwork.%20Business%20Insider%20has%20verified%20revenue%20and%20profit%20with%20documentation.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20did%20my%20college%20undergraduate%20in%20computer%20science.%20I%20had%20written%20little%20bits%20of%20code%20over%20the%20years%20but%20spent%20eight%20years%20as%20a%20freelance%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fux-designer-how-to-make-150000-a-month-freelance-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUX%20designer%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20pivot%20to%20engineering%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-write-better-ai-chatgpt-prompts-according-prompt-engineer-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20prompts%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20started%20a%20podcast%20about%20prompt%20engineering%20in%20March.%20One%20of%20my%20interviewees%20said%20he%20was%20having%20a%20lot%20of%20success%20getting%20work%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fupwork-proposals-features-pitches-jobs-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUpwork%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20give%20it%20a%20try.%20I%20joined%20the%20platform%20and%20offered%20AI%20prompt%20engineering%20for%20large%20language%20models%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-job-losses-freelance-ai-upwork-fiverr-writing-artificial-intelligence-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Claude%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-author-time-boucher-midjourney-ai-novels-books-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMidjourney%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20prompts%20need%20to%20be%20very%20clear.%20There%20are%20three%20concepts%20that%20I%20find%20particularly%20useful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Give%20the%20chatbot%20a%20role%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20need%20to%20tell%20the%20large%20language%20model%20what%20type%20of%20person%20they%20are%20or%20their%20job.%20If%20you%20tell%20it%20to%20%26quot%3Bact%20as%20a%20writer%2C%26quot%3B%20that%20will%20generate%20a%20different%20response%20from%20asking%20it%20to%20%26quot%3Bact%20as%20a%20party%20planner%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bact%20as%20a%20programmer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20ask%20the%20chatbot%3A%20%26quot%3Bact%20as%20a%20party%20planner%20and%20write%20this%20Python%20code%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20will%20produce%20a%20worse%20result%20for%20what%20you%20want%20than%20if%20you%20ask%20it%20to%20do%20the%20same%20task%20as%20a%20developer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Give%20it%20plenty%20of%20context%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20client%20I'm%20currently%20working%20with%20asked%20ChatGPT%20to%20take%20a%20document%20and%20turn%20it%20into%20a%20memo.%20ChatGPT%20didn't%20know%20what%20to%20do%20with%20that%20information.%20Its%20output%20was%20unclear%20and%20random.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20need%20to%20tell%20it%20how%20long%20the%20memo%20needs%20to%20be%20and%20give%20it%20certain%20rules%20to%20follow%20to%20structure%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20if%20you%20wanted%20the%20AI%20to%20read%20an%20article%20and%20summarize%20the%20places%20in%20the%20US%20that%20were%20mentioned%20the%20most%2C%20it's%20not%20enough%20to%20tell%20it%20to%3A%20%26quot%3BRead%20this%20article%20and%20tell%20me%20the%20three%20places%20in%20the%20US%20that%20were%20mentioned%20most.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20you%20could%20prompt%20it%3A%20%26quot%3BRead%20this%20article%20over%2C%20take%20notice%20of%20all%20of%20the%20locations%20that%20are%20mentioned%2C%20go%20through%20all%20of%20those%20locations%2C%20and%20find%20the%20ones%20that%20are%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20From%20that%20list%20of%20locations%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20figure%20out%20the%20ones%20mentioned%20the%20most.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Break%20steps%20into%20multiple%20prompts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOften%2C%20tasks%20are%20more%20complicated%2C%20and%20you%20have%20to%20give%20the%20chatbot%20step-by-step%20instructions%20in%20multiple%20prompts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20previous%20example%2C%20you%20could%20tell%20it%3A%20%26quot%3BRead%20this%20through%20and%20give%20me%20a%20list%20of%20every%20single%20place%20that's%20mentioned%20along%20with%20the%20number%20of%20times%20it's%20mentioned.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20the%20next%20prompt%20could%20be%3A%20%26quot%3BShow%20me%20the%20ones%20in%20the%20United%20States.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20prompt%20after%20that%20could%20be%3A%20%26quot%3BOrganize%20it%20by%20number%20and%20then%20pick%20the%20three%20at%20the%20top%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20whatever%20you%20want%20it%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F3-rules-writing-prompts-chatgpt-ai-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705401799000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a12e7ddcdb354a985705a4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%