20briefly%20to%20discuss%20everything%20that%E2%80%99s%20been%20going%20on%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Ellise%20Shafer%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fnoah-schnapp-israel-hamas-war-backlash-beliefs-misconstrued-1235873454%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fnoah-schnapp-israel-hamas-war-backlash-beliefs-misconstrued-1235873454%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fnoah-schnapp-israel-hamas-war-backlash-beliefs-misconstrued-1235873454%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20killed%20Cedar%20the%20goat%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20goat%20in%20between%20a%20fork%20and%20knife%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65957e0b1c5c7b8c9a0d9260%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%209-year-old%20girl%20tried%20to%20save%20her%20goat%20from%20the%20slaughterhouse.%20What%20happened%20next%20might%20change%20the%20way%20you%20think%20about%20meat.%3Cp%3EiStock%3B%20Rebecca%20Zisser%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECedar%20the%20goat%20was%20sold%20at%20auction%2C%20destined%20for%20the%20dinner%20table.%20But%20his%20owner%2C%20a%209-year-old%20girl%2C%20loved%20him%20too%20much%20for%20that.%20She%20decided%2C%20instead%2C%20to%20save%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20the%20sheriff%20came%20and%20took%20Cedar%20to%20the%20slaughterhouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20might've%20heard%20about%20this%20story.%20It%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Flawsuit-police-seized-girls-pet-goat-cedar-after-auction-dispute-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elit%20up%20the%20news%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20spring%2C%20and%20then%20again%20in%20November%20because%20the%20girl's%20family%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20%E2%80%94%20the%20mere%20existence%20of%20which%20serves%20as%20a%20spoiler%20to%20you%2C%20a%20sophisticated%20consumer%20of%20news%2C%20that%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20bad%20stuff%20went%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20member%20of%20her%20local%20chapter%20of%20the%20century-old%20agricultural%20education%20group%204-H%2C%20the%20girl%20%E2%80%94%20let's%20follow%20the%20lawsuit%20and%20call%20her%20%26quot%3BE%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20raised%20a%20goat.%20She%20was%20supposed%20to%20feed%20it%2C%20care%20for%20it%2C%20and%20then%20sell%20it%20at%20the%20Shasta%20District%20Fair%2C%20in%20Northern%20California.%20Thousands%20of%20children%20participate%20in%204-H's%20livestock%20projects%20every%20year%3B%20they%20raise%20farm%20animals%20and%20sell%20them%2C%20learning%20about%20cows%20and%20pigs%20and%20sheep%20and%20goats%2C%20and%20how%20we%20turn%20them%20into%20meat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EE%20raised%20the%20goat%20as%20planned%2C%20and%20brought%20it%20to%20the%20auction.%20But%20somewhere%20along%20the%20way%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bit%26quot%3B%20had%20become%20a%20him.%20And%20when%20it%20came%20time%20for%20E%20to%20hand%20Cedar%20over%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20his%20new%20owner%2C%20who%20would%20serve%20him%20up%20at%20the%20annual%204-H%20barbecue%2C%20the%20kid%20wouldn't%20let%20go%20of%20the%20kid.%20Sobbing%2C%20E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebegged%20her%20mother%20not%20to%20make%20her%20give%20the%20goat%20up%20for%20slaughter.%20Cedar%20wasn't%20meat.%20He%20was%20her%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20no%20one%20who%20tends%20to%20animals%20wants%20to%20send%20a%20creature%20they've%20raised%20from%20birth%20to%20its%20death.%20But%20that's%20part%20of%20what%204-H%20is%20designed%20to%20teach%20kids.%20It's%20the%20system.%20Animals%20are%20living%20things%20that%20become%20meat.%20That's%20what%20farms%20do.%20It's%20how%20things%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20here%20was%20E%2C%20in%20tears.%20It's%20a%20scene%20that's%20reenacted%20every%20year%20at%20county%20fairs%20across%20the%20land%2C%20a%20rite%20of%20passage%20in%20agricultural%20communities%20right%20up%20there%20with%20spring%20planting%20and%20horse%20shows.%20And%20when%20a%20child%20gets%20emotionally%20distressed%20over%20the%20fulfillment%20of%20a%20commitment%2C%20it's%20lesson%20time.%20A%20parent's%20moral%20agency%20is%20at%20stake.%20It's%20an%20opportunity%20to%20convey%20the%20concepts%20of%20responsibility%2C%20mercy%2C%20and%20justice%2C%20to%20explain%20the%20kind%20of%20world%20we%20want%20and%20the%20kind%20of%20world%20we%20have.%20It's%20a%20teachable%20moment%20%E2%80%94%20though%20reasonable%20people%20can%20disagree%20on%20what%2C%20exactly%2C%20to%20teach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20goat%20pens%20at%20the%20Shasta%20fairground%2C%20E's%20mom%2C%20Jessica%20Long%2C%20said%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20well%2C%20whoooo%20boy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20how%20you%20feel%20about%20eating%20meat%2C%20the%20Longs'%20lawsuit%20may%20wind%20up%20putting%20How%20Things%20Are%20on%20trial.%20By%20holding%20on%20to%20Cedar%2C%20E%20unwittingly%20picked%20a%20fight%20with%20the%20entire%20agriculture-industrial%20complex.%20She%20may%20have%20lost%20the%20battle%2C%20but%20she%20started%20a%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%206%20million%20kids%20belong%20to%204-H%2C%20which%20bills%20itself%20as%20America's%20largest%20youth-development%20organization.%20Only%20a%20sliver%20of%20them%20raise%20animals%3B%20that's%20a%20major%20project%20that%20costs%20money%20and%20time%20and%20requires%20more%20space%20than%20the%20average%20backyard.%20In%20rural%20parts%20of%20America%2C%20though%2C%20it%20knits%20the%20community%20together.%20Usually%2C%20when%20a%20child%20sells%20an%20animal%20at%20the%20county%20fair%2C%20some%20local%20macher%20buys%20it%20for%20more%20than%20its%20market%20value.%20The%20child%20puts%20the%20money%20away%20for%20college%2C%20a%20new%20computer%2C%20whatever.%20The%20littlest%20kids%20always%20cry%3B%20the%20big%20kids%20do%2C%20too%2C%20but%20less.%20Circle%20of%20life.%20And%2C%20sure%2C%20sometimes%20the%20kids%20don't%20go%20through%20with%20it%2C%20and%20mom%20and%20dad%20go%20home%20with%20Bobo%20the%20hog%20as%20a%20pet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20girl%20in%20overalls%20and%20boots%20plays%20with%20a%20small%20white%20goat%20with%20black%20neck%20and%20ears%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659709f6ec62ab5daf80c1db%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENine-year-old%20E%20came%20to%20think%20of%20Cedar%20the%20goat%20as%20a%20pet.%20County%20officials%20insisted%20he%20was%20meat.%3Cp%3ELong%20family%2FAdvancing%20Law%20for%20Animals%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECedar%20went%20for%20the%20handsome%20price%20of%20%24903.%20His%20buyers%20were%20State%20Assemblywoman%20Megan%20Dahle%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20State%20Sen.%20Brian%20Dahle.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20the%20sale%2C%20in%20June%202022%2C%20Brian%20Dahle%20was%20the%20Republican%20candidate%20for%20governor%20of%20California.%20Five%20months%20later%2C%20he%20lost%20to%20Gavin%20Newsom%20in%20a%20landslide%20of%20epic%20proportions%2C%20further%20acquainting%20him%20with%20the%20concept%20of%20a%20sacrificial%20goat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJessica%20Long%20knew%20that%20reneging%20on%20the%20sale%20would%20cause%20trouble%20in%20her%20small%20town.%20So%20she%20sent%20Cedar%20away%20to%20a%20farm%20where%20he%20could%20run%20and%20play%20with%20other%20goats.%20(Seriously.)%20In%20a%20series%20of%20emails%20and%20calls%2C%20she%20explained%20to%20Dahle%20what%20had%20happened%20and%20offered%20to%20repay%20his%20%24903.%20Dahle%20said%20he%20was%20willing%20to%20let%20it%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELong%20made%20the%20same%20offer%20to%20the%20Shasta%20District%20Fair%2C%20which%20was%20entitled%20to%20about%20%2463%20of%20the%20sale.%20But%20the%20fair%20%E2%80%94%20and%20its%20oversight%20agency%2C%20the%20California%20Department%20of%20Food%20and%20Agriculture%20%E2%80%94%20was%20having%20none%20of%20it.%20%26quot%3BThe%20fair%20industry%20is%20set%20up%20to%20teach%20our%20youth%20responsibility%20and%20for%20the%20future%20generations%20of%20ranchers%20and%20farmers%20to%20learn%20the%20process%20and%20effort%20it%20takes%20to%20raise%20quality%20meat%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20fair's%20CEO%20told%20Long.%20%26quot%3BMaking%20an%20exception%20for%20you%20will%20only%20teach%20our%20youth%20that%20they%20do%20not%20have%20to%20abide%20by%20the%20rules%20that%20are%20set%20up%20for%20all%20participants.%26quot%3B%20The%20person%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20fair's%204-H%20barbecue%20claimed%20the%20goat%20was%20now%20stolen%20property.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELong's%20lawsuit%20disputes%20that%20characterization.%20For%20one%20thing%2C%20minors%20in%20California%20are%20allowed%20to%20back%20out%20of%20any%20contract%2C%20no%20questions%20asked.%20And%20for%20another%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20figure%20how%20Long%20and%20her%20daughter%20%26quot%3Bstole%26quot%3B%20a%20goat%20they%20never%20relinquished%20ownership%20of.%20Cedar%20was%20suspended%20between%20pet%20and%20meat%2C%20between%20old%20owner%20and%20new.%20His%20contractual%20status%20was%20that%20of%20a%20no-man's%20goat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELong%20sent%20multiple%20letters%20to%20the%20fair%20asserting%20ownership%20of%20Cedar%20and%20offering%20to%20pay%20everyone's%20expenses.%20She%20also%20indicated%20her%20willingness%20to%20turn%20the%20whole%20mess%20over%20to%20civil%20court%2C%20where%20it%20could%20be%20decided%20under%20the%20vicissitudes%20of%20contract%20law.%20But%20thanks%20in%20part%20to%20viral%20posts%20on%20Twitter%20and%20Instagram%20%E2%80%94%20like%20one%20from%20Bleating%20Hearts%20Farm%20and%20Sanctuary%20in%20Napa%2C%20which%20offers%20%26quot%3Ban%20alternative%20outcome%26quot%3B%20for%20children%20who%20don't%20want%20to%20send%20their%20raised%20farm%20animals%20to%20%26quot%3Bfatal%20auctions%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20Cedar's%20plight%20was%20becoming%20national%20news.%20So%20the%20county%20fair%20swung%20into%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fair%20called%20the%20sheriff.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sheriff%20didn't%20seem%20to%20have%20much%20interest%20in%20airy%20legal%20arguments%20about%20ownership.%20His%20deputies%2C%20armed%20with%20a%20search%20warrant%2C%20immediately%20gassed%20up%20a%20black-and-white%20and%20drove%20a%20couple%20of%20hundred%20miles%20south%2C%20to%20seize%20Cedar%20from%20the%20Bleating%20Hearts%20sanctuary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Cedar%20wasn't%20there!%20Bleating%20Hearts%20had%20just%20been%20'gramming%20about%20him%20in%20solidarity.%20Cedar%20was%20actually%20holed%20up%20in%20a%20totally%20different%20sanctuary%2C%20Billy's%20Mini%20Farm%20in%20Sonoma%2C%20one%20valley%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deputies%20headed%20to%20the%20second%20location.%20And%20even%20though%20they%20didn't%20have%20a%20warrant%20covering%20Billy's%20farm%2C%20its%20owner%20gave%20up%20the%20goat.%20The%20deputies%20then%20brought%20Cedar%20back%20to%20the%20Shasta%20fairgrounds%2C%20the%20place%20where%20he%20had%20been%20sold%20for%20meat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20what%20happened%20next%2C%20no%20one%20is%20saying.%20On%20July%2028%2C%2020%20days%20after%20Cedar%20was%20seized%20in%20the%20daring%20goat-farm%20raid%2C%20an%20assistant%20at%20the%20county%20texted%20his%20boss%20that%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Bkilling%20goat%20today%20finally.%26quot%3B%20All%20they%20were%20waiting%20for%2C%20apparently%2C%20was%20approval%20from%20the%20Shasta%20County%20district%20attorney.%20It's%20not%20clear%20whether%20Cedar%20was%20actually%20eaten%2C%20or%20whether%20he%20was%20just%20slaughtered%20to%20send%20a%20message%20to%20anyone%20foolish%20enough%20to%20treat%20a%20farm%20animal%20like%20a%20pet.%20But%20whoever%20knows%20his%20fate%20isn't%20talking.%20Cedar%20wasn't%20just%20killed.%20He%20was%20%3Cem%3Edisappeared%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20sense%20of%20incredulous%20rage%20you're%20feeling%20right%20now%20at%20the%20fact%20that%20adults%20in%20authority%20spent%20thousands%20of%20taxpayer%20dollars%20and%20days%20of%20law-enforcement%20time%20in%20service%20of%20killing%20a%20child's%20pet%3F%20That's%20why%20this%20story%20went%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20avatars%20of%20the%20American%20farming%20industry%20were%20shocked%20at%20the%20fair's%20rule-bound%20response%20to%20a%20child's%20change%20of%20heart.%20%26quot%3BReasoned%20adults%20might%20bend%20the%20rules%20for%20a%20little%20girl%20and%20her%20pet%20goat.%20That%20didn't%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.drovers.com%2Fopinion%2Fgirl-goat-and-law-shasta-county-ca-boondoggle%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ethe%20beef%20trade%20journal%20Drovers%20pointed%20out%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BMore%20important%20for%20livestock%20producers%20is%20how%20the%20Shasta%20County%20Fair%20and%20the%20Shasta%20County%20sheriff%20%E2%80%94%20both%20unencumbered%20by%20intelligence%20%E2%80%94%20created%20a%20bonanza%20for%20animal%20rights%20zealots.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20is%2C%20indeed%2C%20how%20my%20family%20took%20the%20news.%20We're%20no%20zealots.%20We%20eat%20meat%20in%20our%20house.%20My%20children%20have%20been%20active%20in%20our%20local%204-H%20chapter%2C%20and%20my%20wife%20grew%20up%20raising%20hogs%20for%20hers.%20Her%20sisters%20did%204-H%20livestock%20programs%2C%20too%20%E2%80%94%20sheep%2C%20goats%2C%20rabbits.%20I've%20seen%20my%20wife%20cry%20tears%20of%20both%20joy%20and%20sympathy%20watching%20children%20auction%20their%20animals%20at%20a%20county%20fair%2C%20and%20the%20story%20of%20Cedar%20and%20his%20little%20girl%20shocked%20her%20%E2%80%94%20not%20for%20what%20it%20said%20about%20animal%20rights%2C%20but%20because%20of%20the%20manifest%20absence%20of%20mercy%20for%20a%209-year-old%20child.%20The%20ethics%20of%20raising%20animals%20to%20be%20food%20are%20tough%3B%20the%20ethics%20around%20the%20treatment%20of%20a%20child%20seem%20clearer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20could%20have%20said%3A%20Oh%2C%20sorry%2C%20little%20girl%2C%20we'll%20let%20you%20have%20your%20goat%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Leslie%20Irvine%2C%20a%20sociologist%20at%20the%20University%20of%20California%20at%20Irvine%20who%20studies%20people's%20relationships%20with%20their%20pets.%20Irvine%20has%20done%20key%20work%20in%20understanding%20how%204-H%20livestock%20projects%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1163%2F106311110X12586086158402%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Echange%20kids'%20understanding%20of%20animals%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20how%20they%20learn%20to%20make%20a%20distinction%2C%20over%20time%2C%20between%20companion%20animals%20and%20%26quot%3Bsentient%20commodities%2C%26quot%3B%20over%20which%20humans%20have%20mastery.%20As%20young%20children%20watch%20older%20kids%20go%20through%20the%20process%2C%20they%20also%20learn%20to%20modulate%20their%20emotions.%20%26quot%3BThey%20learn%20that%20only%20babies%20cry%2C%26quot%3B%20Irving%20says.%20%26quot%3BThey%20see%20that%20the%20older%20kids%20aren't%20crying%20when%20their%20animals%20are%20sold%2C%20and%20they've%20got%20all%20this%20money%20they%20can%20put%20toward%20college.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20all%20this%20bellyaching%20over%20a%20goat%20seems%20wimpy.%20It's%20not%20as%20if%20lions%20spend%20much%20intellectual%20effort%20parsing%20their%20relationship%20with%20antelopes.%20But%20then%20again%2C%20lions%20don't%20run%20a%20global%20industry%20that%20kills%20300%20million%20cattle%20and%2070%20billion%20chickens%20every%20year.%20It's%20our%20capacity%20for%20ethical%20reflection%20%E2%80%94%20combined%20with%20our%20ability%20to%20organize%20slaughter%20on%20a%20mass%20scale%20%E2%80%94%20that%20sets%20us%20apart%20from%20other%20predators.%20Humans%20are%20the%20only%20creatures%20capable%20of%20seeing%20different%20animals%20as%20having%20different%20statuses%20under%20different%20contexts%2C%20laborer%20or%20pet%20or%20food.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Long%20family%20had%20a%20relationship%20with%20Cedar%20that%20can't%20be%20measured.%20They%20loved%20him%20like%20a%20dog%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Ryan%20Gordon%2C%20their%20attorney.%20%26quot%3BBut%20to%20the%20fair%2C%20fundamentally%2C%20Cedar%20wasn't%20even%20Cedar.%20He%20was%20just%20cuts%20of%20meat%20worth%20%2463.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20that%20humans%20have%20a%20total%2C%20God-given%20mastery%20over%20other%20animals%20is%20called%20dominionism.%20But%20the%20people%20who%20make%20a%20living%20raising%20livestock%20tend%20to%20have%20a%20more%20nuanced%20attitude.%20One%20of%20Irving's%20former%20students%2C%20Colter%20Ellis%2C%20has%20shown%20that%20cattle%20ranchers%20feel%20a%20keen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1111%2Ftsq.12047%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eduty%20of%20care%20for%20their%20animals%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20often%20regret%20that%20their%20efforts%20lead%20to%20the%20death%20of%20those%20animals.%20Ranchers%20sometimes%20develop%20so%20much%20affection%20for%20a%20particular%20steer%2C%20goat%2C%20or%20sheep%20that%20they%20keep%20it%20out%20of%20the%20slaughterhouse%20%E2%80%94%20transforming%20it%2C%20in%20other%20words%2C%20from%20commodity%20to%20pet.%20But%20generally%2C%20ranchers%20see%20death%20as%20part%20of%20life%2C%20a%20consequence%20of%20the%20responsibility%20to%20feed%20a%20hungry%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22white%20goat%20on%20left%20with%20little%20girl%20seated%20cross-legged%20to%20his%20right%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6424b400b643e80019df6cc6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22367%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhen%20E%20decided%20to%20keep%20Cedar%2C%20local%20officials%20treated%20it%20as%20an%20existential%20threat%20to%20their%20agricultural%20way%20of%20life.%20%3Cp%3ELong%20family%2FAdvancing%20Law%20for%20Animals%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELong's%20daughter%20clearly%20hadn't%20internalized%20that%20lesson%20yet.%20In%20fact%2C%204-H%20doesn't%20even%20claim%20to%20teach%20it.%20%26quot%3BWe%20strongly%20believe%20that%20animal%20science%20projects%20provide%20opportunities%20for%20youth%20to%20develop%20responsibility%2C%20patience%2C%20and%20understanding%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20organization%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20it%20issued%20in%20response%20to%20Cedar's%20case.%20%26quot%3BThe%20programs%20do%20not%20advance%20a%20singular%20point%20of%20view%2C%20but%20empower%20young%20people%20to%20ask%20questions%2C%20think%20for%20themselves%2C%20create%20real-world%20solutions%2C%20and%20lead%20their%20peers.%26quot%3B%20It's%20not%20killing%20animals%20that%204-H%20teaches.%20It's%20%3Cem%3Ereflecting%20%3C%2Fem%3Eabout%20killing%20animals%2C%20and%20what%20it%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20consideration%2C%20E%20decided%20that%20Cedar%20wasn't%20food.%20%26quot%3BHow%20many%20urban%20people%2C%20people%20in%20cities%2C%20have%20actually%20seen%20a%20pig%20or%20a%20goat%20at%20that%20girl's%20age%3F%26quot%3B%20says%20Charlie%20Thieriot%2C%20who%20until%20recently%20ran%20Llano%20Seco%20Meats%2C%20a%20heritage%20pork%20producer%20that%20focused%20on%20sustainability%20and%20ethics.%20%26quot%3BShe%20has%20done%20all%20I%20could%20ask%20a%20fellow%20human%20to%20do%2C%20which%20is%20to%20understand%20the%20animal%20before%20you%20eat%20it.%20And%20if%20you%20decide%20not%20to%20eat%20it%2C%20more%20power%20to%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20adults%20in%20charge%20of%20Shasta's%204-H%20barbecue%20and%20county%20fair%20clearly%20didn't%20see%20things%20that%20way.%20They%20could've%20backed%20Jessica%20Long's%20parenting%20play.%20Instead%20they%20deployed%20the%20cops.%20Maybe%20it%20was%20just%20another%20example%20of%20petty%20martinets%20deploying%20their%20authoritarian%20mindset%20against%20children%20%E2%80%94%20like%20the%20Texas%20school%20administrators%20and%20district%20attorneys%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.texasobserver.org%2Fprosecutors-wont-drop-charges-against-brownsville-isd-honor-student%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eput%20an%2011-year-old%20in%20solitary%20confinement%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20the%20Mississippi%20judge%20who%20sentenced%20a%2010-year-old%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fus-news%2F2023%2Fdec%2F14%2Fblack-child-urinating-mississippi-kobe-bryant-assignment-probation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ethree%20months'%20probation%20for%20peeing%20outside%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20bad%20as%20those%20cases%20are%2C%20I%20think%20there's%20more%20going%20on%20here.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20Cedar%2C%20these%20small-town%20community%20leaders%20from%20an%20agricultural%20area%20were%20reacting%20to%20something%20they%20viewed%20as%20an%20existential%20threat.%20They%20clung%20to%20their%20rulebook%20to%20protect%20their%20way%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20one%20hand%2C%20this%20is%20a%20civil-rights%20dispute%20over%20private%20property%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Gordon%2C%20the%20attorney%20for%20the%20Longs.%20%26quot%3BBut%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20by%20trying%20to%20save%20Cedar%2C%20the%20Longs%20disturbed%20the%20order%20of%20things.%20Cedar%20was%20livestock%2C%20and%20many%20people%20can't%20even%20conceive%20that%20livestock%20like%20Cedar%20can%20be%20something%20more%20than%20food.%20That's%20why%20agricultural%20interests%20in%20the%20government%20fought%20this%20issue%20so%20hard.%26quot%3B%20(The%20California%20Department%20of%20Food%20and%20Agriculture%2C%20the%20Shasta%20fair%2C%20and%20the%20county%20sheriff%20all%20declined%20my%20requests%20for%20comment.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20doesn't%20seem%20that%20Jessica%20Long%20and%20her%20daughter%20intended%20to%20level%20a%20critique%20of%20people%20in%20power%2C%20or%20the%20way%20they%20treat%20livestock.%20Long's%20entreating%20letters%20to%20them%20insist%20that%20they%20did%20not.%20Yet%20the%20state%20food%20and%20agriculture%20department%20has%20countersued%20Long%2C%20and%20in%20late%20December%20her%20attorneys%20filed%20a%20counter%20to%20the%20countersuit%2C%20calling%20it%20an%20attempt%20at%20intimidation.%20E's%20tears%20raised%20fundamental%20questions%2C%20and%20now%20they'll%20get%20asked%20in%20court.%20Those%20questions%20deserve%20an%20honest%20answer.%20Do%20things%20have%20to%20be%20this%20way%3F%20Do%20we%20care%20for%20animals%20in%20an%20ethical%20way%3F%20I%20don't%20know.%20But%20no%20one%20%E2%80%94%20neither%20human%20nor%20goat%20%E2%80%94%20should%20be%20punished%20for%20asking.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fadam-rogers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAdam%20Rogers%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcedar-the-goat-pet-county-fair-killed-slaughter-california-meat-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705400701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65957dd9ec62ab5daf804546%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcedar-the-goat-pet-county-fair-killed-slaughter-california-meat-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20little%20girl%20decided%20to%20save%20her%20goat%20from%20the%20slaughterhouse.%20Then%20the%20sheriff%20showed%20up.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22arogers%40businessinsider.com%20(Adam%20Rogers)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcedar-the-goat-pet-county-fair-killed-slaughter-california-meat-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Dear%20Car%20Owners%2C%20'Buy%20One%2C%20Get%20One%20Free'%20Is%20Not%20For%20This%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EI%20want%20Ram%20Rajya%20in%20Delhi.%20This%20utopian%20state%20of%20my%20dreams%20that%20has%20eluded%20Indians%20for%20several%20millennia%20will%20have%20its%20Lakshman-Rekha%20to%20define%20spaces%20that%20nobody%20can%20encroach%20upon.%20Especially%20not%20those%20who%20think%20that%20the%20universe%20is%20their%20parking%20lot.%20In%20Delhi%2C%20parking%20disputes%20are%20as%20old%20and%20serious%20as%20the%20metaphorical%20ones%20between%20good%20and%20evil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20residential%20area%20in%20Delhi%2C%20or%20any%20other%20city%20in%20India%2C%20is%20immune%20to%20parking%20disputes%20that%20can%20easily%20lead%20to%20violence%20and%20even%20fatalities.%20Interestingly%2C%20in%20most%20cases%2C%20neither%20party%20has%20a%20legal%20right%20over%20the%20space%20they%20fiercely%20fight%20for.%20Just%20like%20two%20college%20Romeos%20fighting%20over%20a%20girl%2C%20who%20is%20unaware%20of%20their%20very%20existence.%20It%20is%20both%20amusing%20and%20appalling%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20root%20of%20all%20parking-related%20evils%20in%20India%20is%20the%20assumption%20that%20a%20plot%20of%20public%20land%20is%20allotted%20to%20a%20person%20the%20moment%20s%2Fhe%20buys%20a%20car%20or%20two-wheeler.%20As%20the%20newly%20procured%20vehicle%20is%20protected%20with%20waterproof%20covers%2C%20this%20plot%20of%20land%20is%20protected%20with%20big%20potted%20plants%2C%20chains%2C%20vigilance%20of%20liveried%20or%20mufti-clad%20'guards'%2C%20or%20even%20ancient%20scooters%20and%20mopeds%20that%20are%20resurrected%20solely%20for%20this%20purpose.%20Needless%20to%20say%2C%20all%20of%20it%20is%20illegal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20outrageous%2C%20however%2C%20is%20that%20this%20illegal%20occupation%20gets%20more%20brazen%20and%20descends%20into%20criminality%20with%20time%2C%20but%20nobody%20views%20it%20as%20such.%20The%20longer%20you%20have%20squatted%20over%20a%20piece%20of%20land%20near%20your%20house%2C%20shop%2C%20or%20office%2C%20the%20stronger%20your%20right%20becomes.%20This%20illegally%20procured%20plot%20becomes%20an%20annexe%20to%20your%20(hopefully)%20legally%20procured%20residential%20or%20commercial%20structure.%20Not%20only%20that%2C%20it%20becomes%20an%20extension%20of%20your%20body%2C%20equally%20inviolable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20civic%20and%20police%20authorities%20at%20least%20pretend%20to%20resolve%20encroachment%20issues%20in%20some%20commercial%20and%20official%20areas%2C%20they%20are%20mostly%20clueless%2C%20often%20intentionally%20so%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20residential%20areas.%20While%20there%20is%20a%20fee%2C%20however%20nominal%2C%20for%20accessing%20parking%20spots%20in%20and%20around%20markets%20and%20office%20complexes%2C%20the%20loot%20of%20public%20spaces%20continues%20unabated%20in%20residential%20areas.%20Somehow%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20paying%20either%20in%20the%20form%20of%20building%20or%20purchasing%20parking%20spaces%20is%20alien%20to%20even%20the%20wealthiest%20members%20of%20Delhi%20society.%20The%20only%20principle%20at%20work%20here%20is%20'buy%20one%20(car)%2C%20get%20one%20(parking%20spot)%20free'.%20Despite%20access%20to%20a%20relatively%20robust%20public%20transport%20system%2C%20people%20in%20Delhi%20have%20continued%20to%20expand%20their%20fleet%20of%20cars%20and%20dutifully%20contributed%20to%20air%20pollution%20and%20congestion%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impunity%20with%20which%20car%20owners%20deprive%20others%20of%20their%20right%20of%20way%2C%20whether%20on%20the%20road%20or%20off%20it%2C%20is%20heightened%20by%20the%20negligence%20and%20corruption%20of%20authorities%20at%20one%20level%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20planning%20at%20the%20policy%20level.%20Police%20resolve%20most%20parking%20disputes%2C%20where%20physical%20violence%20hasn't%20occurred%2C%20by%20handing%20over%20more%20spaces%20to%20the%20warring%20parties.%20X%20to%20park%20in%20front%20of%20their%20house%2C%20Y%20to%20park%20under%20a%20tree%20five%20metres%20away.%20Everyone%20is%20happy.%20Encroachment%20begets%20further%20encroachment.%20To%20be%20fair%2C%20the%20severely%20overburdened%20police%20cannot%20be%20expected%20to%20do%20a%20lot%20more%20than%20minimising%20the%20chances%20of%20violent%20conflicts%20in%20such%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20encroachers%20rely%20on%20their%20strength%20in%20numbers%20when%20challenged%2C%20many%20are%20suave%20enough%20to%20con%20the%20challenger%20with%20legalese%20if%20the%20time-tested%20intimidation%20tactics%20do%20not%20work.%20One%20such%20encroacher%20had%20the%20temerity%20to%20shout%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20the%20easement%20rights%26quot%3B%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20basis%20of%20their%20ownership%20claim.%20In%20a%20country%20with%20limited%20legal%20literacy%2C%20such%20confident%20proclamations%20get%20the%20job%20done.%20But%20why%20even%20go%20there%20when%20the%20classic%2C%20%26quot%3BDo%20you%20know%20who%20I%20am%26quot%3B%20works%20as%20a%20potent%20weapon%3F%20For%20further%20serious%20confrontations%2C%20there's%20the%20gun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Delhi%20continues%20to%20grow%20bigger%2C%20dirtier%2C%20and%20angrier%2C%20this%20colossus%20of%20everyday%20impunity%20needs%20to%20be%20dismantled%2C%20one%20arm%20at%20a%20time%20lest%20the%20city%20implodes.%20At%20the%20policy%20level%2C%20the%20use%20of%20public%20land%20for%20private%20parking%20should%20be%20outlawed%2C%20subject%20to%20severe%20punishment.%20Zero%20exceptions.%20Police%20should%20be%20incentivised%20for%20on-spot%20fines%20and%20vehicle%20seizures%20for%20repeat%20offenders.%20Civil%20authorities%20are%20often%20interested%20in%20headline-making%20big%20plans%20and%20moves.%20Instead%20of%20focusing%20solely%20on%20long-term%20mega%20projects%20of%20big%20parking%20plazas%2C%20due%20attention%20needs%20to%20be%20paid%20to%20developing%20neighbourhood%20parking%20lots%20and%20garages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20city%20can%20fix%20its%20parking%20issues%2C%20many%20other%20problems%20will%20automatically%20be%20solved.%20Hopefully%2C%20the%20non-availability%20of%20free%20land%20will%20dissuade%20people%20from%20expanding%20motor%20fleets%2C%20to%20begin%20with.%20Delhi%20boasts%20of%20some%20of%20the%20widest%20urban%20roads%20in%20the%20country%2C%20they'll%20finally%20be%20used%20to%20capacity.%20Motor%20thefts%20can%20come%20down%20with%20well-monitored%20legitimate%20parking%20areas.%20When%20the%20roads%20and%20streets%20are%20cleared%20of%20haphazardly%20parked%20vehicles%2C%20they%20can%20be%20cleaned%20more%20efficiently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20city%20where%20everybody's%20father%20is%20somebody%2C%20eliminating%20the%20culture%20of%20entitlement%20is%20a%20battle%20that%20cannot%20be%20fought%20and%20won%20at%20once.%20A%20beginning%2C%20however%2C%20needs%20to%20be%20made%20urgently%20and%20automobile%20encroachment%20is%20a%20low-hanging%20fruit.%20Hopefully%2C%20the%20carrot%20of%20a%20cleaner%2C%20safer%20parking%20space%20that%20encourages%20the%20car%20owner%20to%20undertake%20a%20small%20walk%20to%20keep%20their%20heart%20healthy%20will%20work%2C%20and%20the%20stick%20of%20punishment%20won't%20be%20used!%20Let's%20start%20with%20the%20ego-boosting%20campaign%20'Delhi%20cars%20are%20special%2C%20they%20deserve%20their%20best%20life'.%20Make%20paid%20car%20parks%20into%20status%20symbols%20and%20the%20VIPs%20will%20throng%20them!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20will%20be%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20modern%20Ram%20Rajya.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Nishtha%20Gautam%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20author%20and%20academic.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705400700000%2C%22visu