222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHighberger%20and%20her%20friend%20Carlos%20during%20Paris%20Fashion%20Week.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ash%20Highberger%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20landed%2C%20I%20got%20word%20from%20the%20event's%20organizers%20that%20I%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20work.%20It%20turned%20out%20they're%20very%20selective%20about%20who%20they%20allow%20to%20bring%20in%20professional%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20friend%20and%20I%20realized%20we%20had%20to%20rethink%20the%20entire%20trip.%20He%20was%20working%20and%20didn't%20have%20time%20to%20hang%20out%2C%20and%20his%20partner%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20person%20who%20likes%20to%20live%20like%20a%20local%20when%20he%20travels.%20So%20I%20had%20to%20do%20my%20own%20solo%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20want%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20hotel%20the%20entire%20time.%20I%20wanted%20to%20see%20the%20Eiffel%20Tower%20and%20the%20Louvre%2C%20but%20I%20felt%20nervous%20to%20do%20anything%20truly%20by%20myself.%20All%20of%20a%20sudden%2C%20I%20had%20this%20idea%3A%20What%20is%20an%20easy%20way%20to%20just%20meet%20up%20with%20a%20local%3F%20Tinder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20downloaded%20Tinder%20to%20find%20a%20tour%20guide%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20first%20landed%20in%20Paris%2C%20we%20went%20straight%20to%20the%20train%20station%20and%20entered%20the%20city.%20We%20sat%20at%20a%20coffee%20shop%2C%20enjoyed%20a%20charcuterie%20board%2C%20had%20some%20coffees%2C%20and%20even%20stopped%20at%20a%20little%20grocery%20store%20to%20buy%20cigarettes%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20a%20'when%20in%20Rome'%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20all%20the%20cars%20and%20people%20were%20bustling%20around%2C%20and%20hearing%20a%20foreign%20language%20spoken%20fluently%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20I%20didn't%20know%20what%20anyone%20was%20saying%2C%20but%20it%20sounded%20so%20beautiful%20and%20velvety.%20It%20was%20like%20a%20whole%20new%20world%20that%20was%20very%20fun%20and%20exhilarating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Highberger%20in%20Paris%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a1827b43bb77284b9cbd46%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHighberger%20in%20Paris.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ash%20Highberger%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20even%20have%20Tinder%20in%20the%20States%2C%20so%20when%20downloading%20the%20app%2C%20my%20intention%20was%20not%20romantic.%20I%20just%20wanted%20to%20go%20on%20a%20different%20date%20every%20day%2C%20and%20have%20somebody%20show%20me%20something%20that%20they%20loved%20about%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20expanded%20my%20age%20range%20and%20made%20myself%20available%20to%20both%20men%20and%20women.%20I%20would%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20I'm%20only%20in%20town%20for%20a%20short%20period%2C%20and%20I'm%20just%20looking%20for%20someone%20to%20show%20me%20around.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20my%20experience%20of%20swiping%20with%20people%20was%20mostly%20men%20saying%20things%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BTaxicab%20to%20come%20to%20my%20house%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BAbsolutely%20f%E2%80%94ing%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20learned%20quickly%20that%20some%20people%20were%20very%20romantic.%20There%20were%20a%20couple%20of%20people%20who%20had%20similar%20interests%2C%20but%20they%20also%20ended%20up%20soliciting%20sex.%20In%20the%20first%20couple%20of%20hours%2C%20I%20thought%20that%20this%20probably%20was%20not%20going%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20then%20I%20got%20a%20message%20from%20Raphael.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ERaphael%20seemed%20interesting%20and%20trustworthy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERaphael%20messaged%20me%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20here%20to%20sign%20up%20for%20the%20tour%20guide%20position.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20him%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20would%20you%20do%20if%20you%20were%20here%20for%20the%20first%20day%20ever%3F%26quot%3B%20He%20told%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20go%20eat%20at%20this%20market%2C%20I%20would%20go%20to%20this%20place%2C%20I%20would%20go%20here%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20essentially%20giving%20me%20a%20list%20of%20things%20to%20do%20in%20town.%20I%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BOkay%2C%20finally%20someone%20who%20is%20not%20coming%20at%20me%20in%20an%20overtly%20sexual%20direction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20I%20assumed%2C%20from%20how%20fluently%20he%20spoke%20English%2C%20that%20he%20was%20either%20British%20or%20American.%20Surprisingly%2C%20he%20was%20French.%20He%20explained%20that%20he%20learned%20to%20speak%20English%20by%20watching%20movies%20and%20TV%20series%2C%20and%20also%20by%20listening%20to%20music.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223088%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Highberger%20and%20Raphael%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Eiffel%20Tower.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a1826c43bb77284b9cbd26%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222320%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHighberger%20and%20Raphael%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Eiffel%20Tower.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ash%20Highberger%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20second%20day%20of%20my%20trip%2C%20we%20had%20a%20date%20to%20meet%20at%20the%20Louvre%20and%20went%20on%20a%20big%20walk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20met%20him%2C%20we%20hugged%2C%20and%20he%20felt%20really%20awkward.%20I%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20sorry%2C%20I'm%20used%20to%20hugging%20people%20I%20don't%20know.%26quot%3B%20He%20explained%20that%20in%20France%2C%20people%20kiss%20on%20the%20cheek.%20Then%20he%20leaned%20over%20and%20gave%20me%20two%20kisses.%20I%20blushed%20so%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20our%20walk%2C%20he%20had%20so%20many%20questions%20about%20the%20US%2C%20and%20I%20had%20many%20questions%20about%20France.%20It%20felt%20like%20there%20was%20no%20pressure%20or%20weirdness%20between%20us%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20like%20meeting%20up%20with%20a%20friend.%3