0your%20friends%2C%20seeing%20your%20work%2C%20and%20getting%20a%20glimpse%20of%20where%20you%20sleep%20and%20what%20your%20room%20looks%20like.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverything%20seemed%20new%20and%20exciting%20to%20him.%20I%20remember%20when%20he%20landed%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20he%20wanted%20was%20a%20picture%20of%20himself%20with%20a%20truck%20because%20of%20how%20big%20they%20are.%20He%20sent%20his%20friends%20pictures%20of%20gallons%20of%20milk%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BLook%20at%20how%20much%20milk%20this%20is!%20We%20don't%20have%20this%20in%20France.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20also%20surprised%20by%20how%20much%20time%20Americans%20spend%20in%20the%20car%20commuting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Raphael%20at%20a%20Texas%20thrift%20store.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a18266dcdb354a98573130%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERaphael%20at%20a%20Texas%20thrift%20store.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ash%20Highberger%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20his%20first%20visit%2C%20I%20drove%20him%20to%20the%20airport%20and%20we%20both%20sat%20together%20crying%20for%20an%20hour%20%E2%80%94%20we%20didn't%20want%20him%20to%20go%20home.%20We%20decided%20then%20we'd%20be%20willing%20to%20try%20a%20long-distance%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20eventually%20got%20to%20a%20point%20where%20we%20would%20do%20three%20months%20apart%20at%20maximum.%20He%20would%20either%20come%20to%20Texas%2C%20or%20I%20would%20go%20to%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Highberger%20and%20Raphael%20at%20the%20airport.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a1827c43bb77284b9cbd4d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHighberger%20and%20Raphael%20have%20logged%20thousands%20of%20miles%20visiting%20each%20other.%3Cp%3E