%20restaurants%2C%20the%20hourly%20wage%20is%20slightly%20higher%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.paycor.com%2Fresource-center%2Farticles%2Fcalifornia-minimum-wage%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2416.78%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20program%20should%20have%20been%20phased%20in%20over%20time%20instead%20of%20jumping%20the%20California%20minimum%20wage%20for%20our%20staff%20by%2025%25%20in%20one%20single%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalberg%20said%20with%20the%20minimum%20wage%20starting%20at%20%2420%20an%20hour%20for%20entry-level%20workers%2C%20he'll%20be%20forced%20to%20raise%20wages%20for%20shift%20leaders%20and%20managers%20who%20are%20currently%20making%20about%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20money%20but%20have%20much%20more%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20the%20shift%20leader%20and%20you're%20responsible%20for%20making%20sure%20everyone%20got%20their%20breaks%2C%20you're%20not%20going%20to%20do%20all%20that%20extra%20work%20for%20the%20%5Bsame%5D%20%2420%20minimum%20wage%20%5Bas%5D%20the%20guy%20who%20cooks%20the%20burger%20and%20goes%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20he%20said%20there%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bdomino%20effect%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20upper%20ranks%2C%20who%20are%20going%20to%20demand%20more%20money%20or%20flee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20entry-level%20manager%20is%20now%20going%20to%20want%20more%20than%20%2420%20an%20hour%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAll%20that%20translates%20back%20to%20the%20customer%20having%20to%20pay%20more%20money%20because%20the%20landlords%20aren't%20going%20to%20drop%20the%20rent.%20The%20money%20has%20to%20come%20from%20somewhere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Hiring%20patterns%20will%20change.%20Casual%20dining%20restaurant%20workers%20will%20jump%20ship%20to%20fast-food%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20he's%20not%20hiring%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstro