%20Muslims%20are%20waging%20a%20holy%20war%20by%20producing%20more%20children%20%E2%80%93%20under%20the%20scanner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%20crunch%20the%20numbers%20and%20trawl%20through%20parliamentary%20records%20to%20decode%20whether%20Muslims%20will%20indeed%20outnumber%20over%20a%20billion%20Hindus%20in%20the%20near%20future.%20Chapter%203%20scrutinises%20the%20Hindutva%20claim%20of%20a%20sinister%20Christian%20scheme%20to%20take%20over%20India%20through%20mass%20forced%20conversions.%20Chapter%204%20examines%20the%20theory%20of%20Muslim%20appeasement%2C%20probing%20assertions%20like%20unequal%20availability%20of%20electricity%20on%20Diwali%20and%20Eid%2C%20the%20hajj%20subsidy%2C%20funds%20to%20madrasas%2C%20and%20the%20favourite%20bugbear%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Right%3A%20Muslim%20men%20being%20able%20to%20take%20up%20to%20four%20wives.%20With%20its%20clear-eyed%2C%20scrupulously%20argued%20and%20researched%20approach%2C%20%3Cem%3ELove%20Jihad%20and%20Other%20Fictions%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0is%20an%20indispensable%20antidote%20to%20the%20viral%20falsehoods%20threatening%20to%20tear%20India%20apart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20the%20authors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESreenivasan%20Jain%20is%20a%20New%20Delhi-based%20journalist%20and%20broadcaster.%20In%20a%20career%20spanning%20three%20decades%2C%20he%20has%20reported%20on%20wars%2C%20elections%2C%20insurgencies%2C%20majoritarianism%2C%20and%20corruption%20scandals%20for%20the%20television%20network%20NDTV%20where%20he%20worked%20till%20early%202023.%20His%20investigative%20work%20and%20ground%20reportage%20have%20been%20recognised%20by%20the%20Ramnath%20Goenka%20Awards%2C%20Red%20Ink%20Awards%2C%20and%20New%20York%20Festivals%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMariyam%20Alavi%C2%A0has%20reported%20on%20many%20of%20the%20Hindutva%20conspiracy%20theories%20scrutinized%20in%20this%20book.%20She%20worked%20with%20NDTV%20in%20New%20Delhi%20until%20March%202023%2C%20where%20she%20also%20reported%20on%20the%20economy%2C%20politics%2C%20and%20minority%20rights.%20She%20is%20the%20recipient%20of%20the%20International%20Press%20Institute-India%E2%80%99s%20Award%20for%20Excellence%20in%20Journalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupriya%20Sharma%C2%A0has%20spent%20two%20decades%20covering%20conflict%2C%20politics%2C%20and%20development.%20Her%20reports%20have%20fetched%20several%20honours%2C%20including%20the%20Ramnath%20Goenka%20Awards%20and%20Chameli%20Devi%20Jain%20Award%20for%20Outstanding%20Woman%20Journalist%2C%20among%20others.%20She%20is%20currently%20the%20Executive%20Editor%20of%C2%A0%3Cem%3EScroll%3C%2Fem%3E.%20She%20lives%20in%20Delhi%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705399234000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23164055%2F2EC978D3-90C7-460D-AE0F-2F02A3393076.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fnew-book-debunks-myths-about-love-jihad-muslim-appeasement-and-other-falsehoods-about-minorities%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20its%20clear-eyed%2C%20scrupulously%20argued%20and%20researched%20approach%2C%20Love%20Jihad%20and%20Other%20Fictions%C2%A0is%20an%20indispensable%20antidote%20to%20the%20viral%20falsehoods%20threatening%20to%20tear%20India%20apart.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fnew-book-debunks-myths-about-love-jihad-muslim-appeasement-and-other-falsehoods-about-minorities%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ram%20Temple%20Inauguration%20a%20%E2%80%98Political%20Narendra%20Modi%20Function%E2%80%99%2C%20Says%20Rahul%20Gandhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16152704%2FGD79PDrbEAASkUQ.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChiechama%20(Nagaland)%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3ECongress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20said%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20have%20made%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20on%20January%2022%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20Narendra%20Modi%20function%E2%80%9D%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20the%20Congress%20to%20participate%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20his%20first%20press%20conference%20during%20the%20ongoing%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20which%20entered%20its%20third%20day%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Gandhi%20did%20not%20answer%20whether%20he%20would%20visit%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20during%20the%20yatra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20RSS%20and%20the%20BJP%20have%20made%20the%20January%2022%20function%20a%20political%20Narendra%20Modi%20function.%20It%20has%20become%20a%20RSS-BJP%20function.%20That%20is%20why%20Congress%20president%20(Mallikarjun%20Kharge)%20said%20that%20he%20won%E2%80%99t%20go%20to%20the%20function%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%20reporters%20in%20Chiechama%2C%20Nagaland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20open%20to%20all%20religions%20and%20practices.%20Even%20the%20authorities%20of%20the%20Hindu%20religion%20have%20made%20their%20view%20public%20of%20what%20they%20think%20of%20the%20January%2022%20function.%20It%20is%20difficult%20for%20us%20to%20go%20to%20a%20function%20designed%20around%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20Congress%20in%20a%20statement%20announced%20that%20party%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20former%20party%20president%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20leader%20of%20opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Choudhury%20will%20not%20be%20attending%20the%20grand%20inauguration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20presided%20over%20by%20Modi%20next%20week%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbreaking-congress-declines-invitation-to-ram-temple-inauguration-calls-its-clearly-an-rss-bjp-event%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CBJP-RSS%20event%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20since%20mounted%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fif-congress-is-anti-hindu-are-shankaracharyas-also-anti-hindu%5C%22%3Econcerted%20attack%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Congress%20and%20accused%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20of%20being%20anti-Hindu%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fanti-ram-bjp-invokes-nehru-slams-congress-over-declining-invite-of-ayodhya-temple-event%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Canti-Ram%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20said%20that%20as%20far%20as%20religion%20is%20concerned%2C%20the%20party%20is%20with%20all%20religions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20with%20all%20religions%20and%20we%20have%20made%20it%20clear%20to%20our%20party%20members%20and%20alliance%20members%20that%20whoever%20wishes%20to%20attend%2C%20they%20can%20do%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20veiled%20attack%20on%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20Gandhi%20added%20that%20anyone%20who%20actually%20believes%20in%20religion%20keeps%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpersonal%20relationship%E2%80%9D%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSomeone%20who%20actually%20believes%20in%20religion%20keeps%20a%20personal%20relationship%20with%20it.%20He%20uses%20religion%20in%20his%20life.%20Those%20who%20keep%20a%20public%20relation%20with%20religion%2C%20try%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20it.%20I%20do%20not%20try%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20my%20religion%2C%20I%20have%20no%20interest.%20I%20try%20to%20live%20according%20to%20the%20principles%20of%20religion.%20I%20behave%20nicely%20with%20people%2C%20and%20I%20respect%20them.%20When%20someone%20says%20something%20to%20me%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20respond%20with%20arrogance%2C%20I%20listen%20to%20them.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20spread%20hatred.%20For%20me%2C%20this%20is%20the%20Hindu%20religion.%20I%20follow%20this%20in%20life.%20But%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20wear%20it%20on%20my%20sleeve.%20Those%20who%20do%20not%20believe%20in%20it%20need%20to%20wear%20it%20on%20their%20sleeve%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20also%20said%20that%20the%20ongoing%20yatra%2C%20which%20is%20being%20conducted%20from%20Manipur%20to%20Maharashtra%2C%20will%20cover%206%2C700%20km%20and%20end%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20March%2020%20or%2021.%20While%20it%20is%20the%20biggest%20mass%20outreach%20programme%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20Gandhi%20said%20that%20the%20yatra%20is%20an%20%E2%80%9Cideological%E2%80%9D%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20see%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20as%20well%20placed%20to%20take%20on%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20The%20yatra%20is%20an%20ideological%20one%20to%20place%20many%20issues%20on%20the%20table%20which%20include%20the%20huge%20amount%20of%20injustice%20that%20has%20been%20taking%20place%20across%20the%20country.%20It%20is%20to%20present%20an%20alternative%20vision%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20seat%20sharing%20arrangements%20yet%20to%20be%20finalised%20by%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20and%20alleged%20disagreements%20between%20alliance%20partners%2C%20Gandhi%20said%20that%20the%20process%20is%20ongoing%20and%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20a%20complex%20one%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CStatus%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20is%20very%20good.%20Seat%20sharing%20discussion%20is%20going%20on%20let%E2%80%99s%20see%20where%20it%20ends.%20Discussions%20are%20simple%20and%20not%20complex%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20yatra%2C%20which%20will%20spend%20another%20day%20in%20Nagaland%20before%20moving%20on%20to%20Assam%20later%20this%20week%2C%20began%20in%20Manipur%20which%20has%20been%20in%20the%20grip%20of%20ethnic%20violence%20since%20May%203%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20in%20Manipur%20because%20Manipur%20has%20faced%20gross%20injustice%20including%20widespread%20loss%20of%20life%20and%20property.%C2%A0%20For%20the%20first%20time%20an%20Indian%20state%20is%20witnessin