%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDid%20I%20ask%20you%20what%20you%20have%20said%20to%20whom%3F%E2%80%9D%20Constable%20Rana%20kicked%20at%20the%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSaheb%2C%20Salman%20bhai%20brought%20us%20qorma%20in%20that%20pateela.%20We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20know%20where%20it%20was%20from%20%E2%80%93%20we%20just%20ate%20the%20qorma%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20maulvi%20folded%20his%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHain%3F%20What%20is%20he%20saying%20%E2%80%93%20Salman%20brought%20the%20pateela%3F%E2%80%9D%20the%20ACP%20asked.%20Achche%20Lal%20whispered%20into%20his%20ears%20briefly%20and%20the%20ACP%20frowned.%20%E2%80%9CThen%20you%20should%20have%20caught%20him%20last%20night%20only.%20What%20were%20you%20waiting%20for%3F%20They%20are%20all%20confirming%20that%20Salman%20had%20brought%20them%20the%20pateela%3F%20To%20feed%20them%3F%20Since%20when%20has%20he%20become%20such%20a%20provider%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20called%20out%20to%20the%20maulvi%2C%20%E2%80%9CMaster%20ji%2C%20you%20come%20out%20here%2C%20and%20call%20the%20boys%20also.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20see%20who%20ate%20what.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20this%20time%2C%20a%20small%20crowd%20of%20onlookers%20had%20assembled.%20The%20maulvi%20was%20wailing%2C%20%E2%80%9CHad%20Rahman%20miyan%20been%20alive%2C%20he%20would%20have%20saved%20us.%20Who%20will%20look%20after%20us%20now%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFirst%20you%20steal%20qorma%20from%20a%20dead%20man%20%E2%80%93%20feast%20on%20it%2C%20and%20then%20you%E2%80%99re%20crying%20for%20him%20when%20you%E2%80%99re%20caught%3F%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20shame%3F%E2%80%9D%20ACP%20saheb%20felt%20stirred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20maulvi%20spotted%20Laadley%20in%20the%20crowd.%20%E2%80%9CLaadley%20bhai%2C%20please%20save%20me.%C2%A0%20You%20tell%20Inspector%20saheb%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20done%20nothing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ACP%20half-turned%20towards%20Laadley%2C%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20intervene%20unless%20you%20want%20to%20get%20arrested.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20disturb%20law%20and%20order.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Laadley%20was%20not%20easily%20deterred.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20orphans%2C%20saheb.%20Salman%20has%20grown%20up%20amidst%20them.%20He%20often%20brings%20them%20food.%20Sometimes%2C%20he%20takes%20from%20my%20hotel%20also.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ACP%20seemed%20to%20not%20have%20heard.%20%E2%80%9CCall%20everyone%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20snapped.%20A%20dozen%20boys%20of%20various%20ages%2C%20ranging%20from%20six%20to%2019%20but%20uniformly%20spindly%2C%20stood%20in%20a%20straight%20line%2C%20seeming%20more%20curious%20than%20fearful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMake%20them%20all%20stand%20in%20line%2C%20height%20wise.%20The%20tallest%20ones%20at%20the%20end%20closest%20to%20where%20I%20am%20standing.%20And%2C%20master%20ji%2C%20you%20also%20come%20and%20join%20the%20line%20at%20this%20end%20%E2%80%93%20you%20are%20senior%20most.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20at%20that%20fortuitous%20moment%20that%20Tara%2C%20accompanied%20by%20Jamal%20and%20Habib%2C%20arrived%20at%20the%20madarsa.%20She%20grimaced%20when%20she%20heard%20the%20boys%20being%20asked%20to%20stand%20height%20wise%20in%20a%20straight%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSir%2C%20they%20are%20children!%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWho%20are%20you%2C%20madam%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20the%20ACP%20wearily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20lawyer.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhose%20lawyer%3F%20One%20of%20them%20has%20engaged%20you%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked%20impassively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20only%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20children%20remain%20safe.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20you%20are%20suggesting%20that%20the%20children%20are%20not%20safe%20in%20the%20company%20of%20policemen%3F%E2%80%9D%20the%20ACP%20feigned%20a%20smile.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20this%3F%20What%20is%20happening%20in%20this%20country%3F%20And%20these%20two%20with%20you%3A%20do%20you%20know%20they%20are%20being%20investigated%20for%20conspiracy%3F%20Together%20you%20all%20will%20watch%20over%20us%20as%20we%20try%20to%20carry%20on%20investigations%3F%20Don%E2%80%99t%20try%20to%20browbeat%20the%20police%2C%20Madam.%20It%20will%20cause%20you%20trouble.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ACP%20found%20a%20parapet%20to%20climb%20on%2C%20so%20that%20he%20was%20higher%20than%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20group.%20He%20stood%20there%2C%20arms%20akimbo%2C%20gazing%20at%20the%20crowd%20with%20authority%2C%20and%20gave%20out%20more%20orders%3A%20%E2%80%9CTake%20those%20two%20inside%20to%20identify%20the%20pateela%3B%20then%20seize%20it%20as%20evidence%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20nodded%20at%20Abrar%20and%20Arshad%2C%20then%20turned%20towards%20Tara%3A%20%E2%80%9CMadam%2C%20this%20is%20a%20criminal%20investigation.%20This%20is%20not%20some%20PIL%20matter.%20Please%20stand%20back.%E2%80%9D%20There%20was%20palpable%20tension%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInside%20the%20madarsa%2C%20Abrar%20and%20Arshad%20were%20examining%20the%20pateela%20with%20some%20self-importance.%20%E2%80%9CAye%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20touch.%20It%20is%20evidence.%20Look%20at%20it%20from%20here%20and%20say%2C%E2%80%9D%20snapped%20Rana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYehi%20hai!%20This%20is%20indeed%20our%20big%20pateela.%20They%20have%20washed%20it%20clean.%20Had%20a%20full%20dawat%20on%20my%20qorma%2C%20hain%3F%E2%80%9D%20Abrar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPucca%2C%20it%20is%20our%20pateela%2C%E2%80%9D%20confirmed%20Arshad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EACP%20saheb%20had%20now%20sat%20down%20on%20a%20plastic%20chair.%20It%20may%20have%20been%20the%20same%20one%20that%20Laadley%20had%20earlier%20occupied.%20Or%20it%20may%20have%20been%20another%3B%20Neelkamal%20plastic%20chairs%20were%20easily%20found%20in%20the%20old%20galis.%20Achche%20Lal%20had%20bent%20down%20behind%20him%20in%20order%20to%20speak%20directly%20into%20his%20ears%3A%20%E2%80%9CSir%2C%20I%20have%20already%20recorded%20their%20statements%20last%20night.%20It%20is%20believable%20that%20Salman%20had%20brought%20the%20pateela%20here.%20There%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20be%20any%20direct%20involvement%20of%20these%20people.%20Better%20to%20go%20arrest%20Salman%2C%20sir.%20If%20we%20spend%20too%20much%20time%20at%20the%20madarsa%2C%20it%20will%20become%20an%20issue.%20One%20lawyer%20is%20already%20present%2C%20soon%20the%20media%20will%20come.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20should%20have%20apprehended%20Salman%20last%20night%20itself%2C%20but%20now%20there%20has%20been%20a%20recovery%20from%20the%20madarsa.%20What%20if%20one%20of%20them%20is%20responsible%20and%20he%20absconds%20later%3F%20Where%20will%20you%20go%20about%20finding%20them%3F%E2%80%9D%20ACP%20saheb%20retorted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20keep%20all%20their%20names%20in%20the%20register%2C%20sir.%20There%20is%20no%20direct%20involvement.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EACP%20saheb%20dismissed%20Achche%20Lal%20with%20an%20impatient%20wave%20of%20the%20hand%20and%20motioned%20to%20maulvi%20saheb%20to%20come%20forward.%20%E2%80%9CHaan%20ji%2C%20master%20ji%2C%20how%20did%20Rahman%20miyan%E2%80%99s%20pateela%20come%20to%20be%20in%20your%20kitchen%3F%20Did%20one%20of%20the%20boys%20steal%20it%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaulvi%20saheb%20was%20shaking%20involuntarily.%20He%20let%20out%20a%20sob%2C%20which%20was%20more%20than%20Laadley%20could%20bear%3A%20%E2%80%9CArre%2C%20maulvi%20saheb%2C%20why%20are%20you%20crying%20like%20a%20woman%3F%20ACP%20saheb%20is%20asking%20you%20a%20simple%20question%20%E2%80%93%20just%20answer%20it.%20What%20is%20the%20problem%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ACP%20sighed%20at%20the%20extent%20of%20crowd%20participation%2C%20but%20nodded%20encouragingly%20at%20maulvi%20saheb.%20%E2%80%9CSaheb%2C%20Salman%20bhai%20brought%20qorma.%20He%20said%20you%20all%20have%20not%20had%20qorma%20in%20some%20time%2C%20so%20eat%20it.%20Then%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98Let%20me%20take%20a%20little%20bit%20for%20Naseeban%E2%80%99s%20children%20also.%E2%80%99%20The%20rest%20I%20distributed%20amongst%20all%20the%20boys%2C%20and%20then%20we%20cleaned%20the%20pateela%20and%20left%20it%20in%20the%20kitchen%20thinking%20he%20will%20take%20it%20back.%20That%20is%20all%20I%20know!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAchche%20Lal%2C%20he%20took%20some%20of%20it%20to%20Naseeban%E2%80%99s%20house%20it%20seems.%20Have%20you%20checked%20her%20house%20for%20evidence%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EASI%20Achche%20Lal%20mumbled%20that%20he%20had%20not.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%20miss%20small%20details%20like%20this.%20Whole%20case%20may%20turn%20on%20such%20details%2C%E2%80%9D%20ACP%20saheb%20said%20officiously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSaheb%2C%20Rahman%20miyan%E2%80%99s%20tiffin%20carrier%20was%20also%20missing.%20It%20is%20not%20here%20at%20the%20madarsa%20either.%20He%20must%20have%20taken%20qorma%20in%20it%20to%20Naseeban%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Abrar%20in%20a%20shrill%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalabhadra%20babu%2C%20uncharacteristically%20absent%20thus%20far%2C%20came%20upon%20the%20scene%20just%20then.%20%E2%80%9CArre%2C%20what%20is%20happening%3F%20Nobody%20informed%20me!%20I%20have%20been%20busy%20with%20organising%20the%20consecration%20programme%2C%20bhai.%E2%80%9D%20He%20detached%20himself%20from%20the%20crowd%20and%20approached%20the%20ACP%2C%20a%20little%20awkwardly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EACP%20saheb%20watched%20with%20annoyance%20as%20Balabhadra%20babu%20shuffled%20about%20till%20he%20had%20found%20himself%20a%20matching%20chair%2C%20which%20he%20set%20very%20close%20to%20ACP%20saheb%E2%80%99s%20own%20chair.%20Balabhadra%20babu%20proceeded%20to%20sit%20on%20it%20and%20then%20leant%20forward%2C%20apparently%20to%20whisper%20something%20in%20confidence%20to%20ACP%20saheb.%20He%20seemed%20to%20be%20explaining%20something%20at%20length%20to%20ACP%20saheb.%20ASI%20Achche%20Lal%20who%20was%20standing%20just%20behind%20the%20ACP%20heard%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArre%2C%20the%20tiffin%20carrier%20has%20been%20found%20too!%20It%20is%20with%20Shambhu%2C%20not%20with%20Naseeban%2C%E2%80%9D%20Achche%20Lal%20exclaimed%20loudly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ACP%20turned%20around%20and%20glared%20at%20Achche%20Lal.%20Tara%20found%20her%20moment%20and%20said%20that%20things%20from%20Rahman%20miyan%E2%80%99s%20hotel%20had%20obviously%20been%20taken%20by%20different%20people%2C%20and%20they%20were%20slowly%20turning%20up%20in%20different%20places%2C%20and%20there%20may%20not%20be%20any%20need%20to%20blame%20the%20children%20alone%20and%20to%20keep%20them%20back%20for%20questioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHaan%2C%20I%20agree%20with%20madam.%20Only%20main%20murderer%20has%20to%20be%20found.%20In%20any%20case%2C%20sir%2C%20I%20have%20told%20Shambhu%20to%20wait%20in%20my%20shop.%20Anytime%20sir%20wants%2C%20he%20can%20speak%20to%20him.%20But%20it%20was%20a%20genuine%20mistake%3B%20I%20can%20assure%20you.%20He%20brought%20back%20the%20packet%20thinking%20it%20had%20only%20his%20pateela%20in%20it%2C%20and%20the%20tiffin%20carrier%20also%20happened%20to%20be%20lying%20inside%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Balabhadra%20babu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EACP%20saheb%20weighed%20all%20the%20options%20and%20decided%20to%20not%20make%20arrests%20at%20the%20madarsa%20at%20the%20moment.%20%E2%80%9CTake%20down%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20name%2C%20address%20and%20Aadhar%20number%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20gruffly%2C%20as%20he%20prepared%20to%20lead%20his%20party%20to%20Naseeban%E2%80%99s%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20is%20the%20whole%20mohalla%20walking%20to%20the%20next%20place%3F%20Is%20this%20any%20way%3F%20Somebody%20would%20have%20called%20and%20warned%20Salman%20by%20now%20%E2%80%93%20what%20kind%20of%20investigation%20are%20you%20all%20carrying%20out%3F%20And%20Achche%20Lal%2C%20I%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20expected%20this%20kind%20of%20behaviour%20from%20you!%20You%20announced%20to%20the%20whole%20mohalla%20something%20that%20had%20been%20said%20to%20us%20in%20confidence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20as%20Laadley%20and%20the%20man%20in%20the%20checked%20lungi%2C%20Abrar%20and%20Arshad%2C%20Jamal%2C%20Habib%20and%20Tara%2C%20Balabhadra%20babu%2C%20as%20well%20as%20several%20boys%20from%20the%20madarsa%20walked%20behind%20a%20posse%20of%20policemen%20to%20Naseeban%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20they%20all%20wondered%20for%20the%20first%20time%20whether%20he%20would%20be%20arrested%20for%20Rahman%20miyan%E2%80%99s%20murder.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20there%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20tall%20boy%20from%20the%20madarsa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%2C%20you%20warned%20him%3F%E2%80%9D%20said%20Laadley%20with%20a%20wink.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArre%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20his%20time%20to%20be%20there%20now.%20It%E2%80%99s%20only%20noon%2C%E2%80%9D%20Abrar%20laughed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20at%20some%20point%20Salman%20will%20need%20a%20good%20lawyer%2C%E2%80%9D%20Laadley%20felt.%20%E2%80%9CHis%20mother%20works%20with%20important%20people%2C%20they%E2%80%99ll%20provide%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20his%20companion%20who%20was%20wearing%20a%20checked%20lungi.%20Laadley%20was%20probably%20not%20convinced%20for%20he%20sidled%20up%20to%20Jamal%20and%20Habib%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20madam%E2%80%99s%20full%20name%3F%20Is%20she%20Mohammadan%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%20They%20shrugged%20in%20embarrassment.%20Tara%20heard%20too%2C%20but%20said%20nothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20search%20of%20Naseeban%E2%80%99s%20modest%20quarters%20revealed%20neither%20Salman%20nor%20any%20leftover%20qorma%2C%20but%20the%20police%20did%20recover%20a%20plastic%20folder%20with%20sundry%20certificates%20and%20papers%20belonging%20to%20Rahman%20miyan.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20this%20now%3F%20Has%20he%20stolen%20any%20bank%20papers%3F%E2%80%9D%20ACP%20saheb%20extended%20his%20hand%20for%20the%20folder.%20%E2%80%9CAadhar%2C%20voter%E2%80%99s%20ID%20card%2C%20electricity%20bills%2C%20medical%20bills%2C%20what%20is%20all%20this%E2%80%A6and%20where%20is%20the%20meat%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20must%20have%20been%20eaten%20that%20night%20only.%20Why%20would%20they%20keep%20it%20for%20four%20days%3F%E2%80%9D%20said%20Laadley.%20Naseeban%20and%20her%20children%20admitted%20that%20Salman%20had%20bought%20qorma%20and%20fed%20them%2C%20which%20threw%20Naseeban%E2%80%99s%20husband%20into%20another%20fit%20of%20anger.%20%E2%80%9CBecause%20of%20you%2C%20my%20little%20children%20will%20now%20go%20to%20jail.%20How%20could%20you%20let%20a%20murderer%20feed%20my%20children%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20ranted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDid%20he%20say%20where%20he%20had%20got%20it%20from%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Achche%20Lal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo!%20Four%20pieces%20of%20mutton%20%E2%80%93%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20discuss%20where%20it%20had%20come%20from.%20We%20just%20ate%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Naseeban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20did%20he%20bring%20this%20folder%20full%20of%20Rahman%20miyan%E2%80%99s%20identity%20papers%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20will%20tell%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20old%20Zaitoon%20nani%20had%20hobbled%20across%20with%20Salman%E2%80%99s%20mother%20upon%20hearing%20that%20the%20police%20were%20raiding%20Naseeban%E2%80%99s%20house.%20%E2%80%9COf%20late%2C%20he%20had%20become%20possessed%20with%20the%20idea%20that%20he%20needed%20to%20collect%20certificates%20and%20all%20kinds%20of%20papers.%20I%20suspect%20he%20brought%20these%20without%20realising%20that%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20use%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEveryone%20has%20an%20opinion%2C%E2%80%9D%20muttered%20the%20ACP.%20%E2%80%9CWhere%20is%20Salman%20now%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked%20Salman%E2%80%99s%20mother%20and%20Zaitoon%20nani%20harshly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMust%20be%20in%20the%20bazaar%2C%E2%80%9D%20Salman%E2%80%99s%20mother%20started%20to%20curse%20Naseeban%20and%20cry%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20only%20son%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20she%20sobbed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ACP%20had%20dispatched%20Constable%20Rana%2C%20together%20with%20Abrar%20and%20Arshad%2C%20to%20look%20for%20Salman.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20to%20speak%20to%20this%20Shambhu%20also%2C%20Balabhadra%20babu.%E2%80%9D%20He%20turned%20and%20surveyed%20the%20lingering%20crowd%2C%20%E2%80%9CAchche%20Lal%2C%20will%20this%20crowd%20be%20following%20me%20all%20over%20the%20mohalla%20today%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSir%2C%20let%20them%20come%20if%20they%20want%20to%20come.%20Otherwise%20they%20will%20make%20it%20seem%20as%20if%20there%20is%20some%20big%20conspiracy%20and%20that%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20save%20Shambhu.%20Let%20them%20see%20for%20themselves%20that%20we%20interrogated%20him%20also%20as%20part%20of%20our%20investigation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalabhadra%20babu%20ushered%20everyone%20into%20his%20shop%20with%20great%20formality%20and%20immediately%20sent%20someone%20to%20bring%20%E2%80%98hot%20tea%2C%20first%E2%80%99.%20%E2%80%9CShambhu%20himself%20is%20the%20tea%20champion%2C%20but%20today%20he%20has%20to%20be%20interrogated%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20declared.%20%E2%80%9CI%20told%20him%20that%20it%20was%20a%20grave%20mistake%3B%20he%20should%20not%20have.%20But%20it%20is%20a%20genuine%20case%2C%20sir.%20His%20own%20utensil%20was%20in%20the%20same%20packet.%20It%20was%20a%20death%20scene%2C%20so%20he%20was%20trying%20to%20be%20respectful.%20He%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20poke%20and%20prod.%20He%20quietly%20picked%20up%20his%20packet%20without%20checking%20to%20see%20whether%20there%20was%20anything%20else%20inside.%20Only%20later%20he%20found%20out%20about%20the%20tiffin%20carrier.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20crime%20scene%3B%20body%20was%20still%20lying%20there%20and%20you%20went%20about%20looking%20for%20your%20utensil%3F%20What%20was%20so%20urgent%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20the%20ACP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSir%2C%20I%20had%20to%20make%20the%20day%E2%80%99s%20gulab%20jamun!%20Night%20before%20Jamal%20ji%20had%20ordered%20gulab%20jamun%2C%20so%20I%20sent%20back%20two%20plates.%20Then%20he%20asked%20for%20more%20gulab%20jamun%20and%20chashni%2C%20so%20I%20sent%20the%20pateela%20only%20thinking%20it%E2%80%99ll%20come%20back%20the%20next%20morning.%20Then%20I%20saw%20it%20lying%20there%2C%20washed%2C%20and%20I%20thought%20Arshad%20must%20have%20washed%20and%20kept%20it%20for%20returning%20to%20me%2C%20so%20I%20brought%20it%20back.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamal%20was%20listening%20intently.%20He%20scratched%20his%20nose%20in%20a%20thoughtful%20manner%20and%20looked%20at%20Habib.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDid%20you%20really%20not%20see%20the%20big%20tiffin%20carrier%3F%20How%20big%20was%20your%20packet%20that%20the%20tiffin%20just%20got%20lost%20in%20it%3F%20You%20didn%E2%80%99t%20feel%20its%20weight%20also%3F%E2%80%9D%20the%20ACP%20stood%20very%20close%20to%20Shambhu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMust%20have%20deliberately%20stolen%20it%2C%20sir%2C%E2%80%9D%20called%20out%20Laadley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalabhadra%20babu%20coughed.%20%E2%80%9CACP%20saheb%2C%20why%20would%20he%20steal%20a%20non-veg%20tiffin%20carrier%3F%20He%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20take%20non-veg%20food%2C%20or%20serve%20it%20in%20his%20shop.%20What%20use%20is%20a%20non-veg%20tiffin%20carrier%20to%20us%3F%20He%20came%20and%20informed%20me%20as%20soon%20as%20he%20realised%20his%20mistake.%20Anyway%2C%20I%20am%20certain%20that%20once%20the%20report%20comes%2C%20we%20shall%20find%20out%20that%20it%20was%20not%20even%20murder.%20It%20was%20probably%20gastro%2C%20or%20asthma.%20Rahman%20miyan%20ran%20such%20a%20famous%20hotel%2C%20but%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20eat%20anything%20because%20of%20his%20stomach%20problems.%20And%20his%20asthma%20became%20very%20bad%20in%20the%20winter%20air.%20ACP%20saheb%2C%20our%20humble%20request%20is%3A%20please%20close%20this%20matter%20before%20the%20holy%20consecration%20ceremony.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAre%20you%20saying%20that%20the%20air%20killed%20him%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Tara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20all%20die%20incrementally%20until%20the%20day%20we%20actually%20die%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Balabhadra%20babu%20philosophically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20phone%20rang%20and%20ASI%20Achche%20Lal%20held%20up%20his%20hand%2C%20motioning%20for%20them%20to%20stop%20talking.%20He%20listened%20into%20the%20phone%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSir%2C%20Salman%20has%20been%20apprehended.%20Rana%20has%20detained%20him%20and%20is%20seeking%20your%20permission%20to%20call%20an%20Uber%20to%20take%20him%20to%20the%20police%20station.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAre%20you%20arresting%20Salman%3F%20But%20you%20are%20not%20detaining%20this%20one%20for%20theft%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tara%20motioned%20towards%20Shambhu%20with%20her%20chin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMadam%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20answer%20to%20you%20why%20I%20am%20arresting%20one%20suspect%20and%20not%20arresting%20another.%20Salman%20is%20a%20known%20offender%2C%20Rahman%20miyan%E2%80%99s%20papers%20have%20been%20recovered%20from%20him%2C%20plus%20he%20tried%20to%20abscond.%20And%20let%20me%20tell%20you%20%E2%80%93%20he%20was%20helped%20by%20someone%20from%20the%20madarsa%2C%20those%20%E2%80%98children%E2%80%99%20that%20you%20were%20valiantly%20trying%20to%20save%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20ACP%20tersely%20and%20strode%20out%20of%20the%20shop%2C%20ending%20any%20further%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMadam%2C%20the%20police%20are%20like%20that%20only.%20They%20are%20always%20blaming%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20Laadley%20said%20matter%20of%20factly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalabhadra%20babu%20looked%20at%20Laadley%E2%80%99s%20sullen%20expression%2C%20and%20also%20noted%20Jamal%20and%20Habib%E2%80%99s%20despondent%20faces.%20%E2%80%9CLet%20the%20police%20do%20their%20duty%2C%20It%20is%20not%20right%20to%20keep%20questioning%20like%20this.%20Nobody%20is%20discriminating%20against%20any%20person%20or%20community.%20We%20are%20all%20one.%20Come%2C%20let%20us%20have%20another%20round%20of%20tea%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIsn%E2%80%99t%20it%20time%20to%20close%20the%20shop%20for%20lunch%2C%20Bulbhaddar%20chacha%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Jamal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArre%2C%20where%20is%20the%20time%20for%20lunch%20these%20days%3F%20There%20is%20so%20much%20work%20to%20do.%20Now%20look%20at%20these%20Modi%20masks.%20These%20are%20leftover%20stock%20from%20the%20previous%20election%2C%20but%20in%20tip-top%20condition%2C%E2%80%9D%20Balabhadra%20babu%20picked%20up%20a%20paper%20mask%20and%20put%20it%20on.%20Suddenly%20they%20saw%20Modi%20Ji%20beaming%20at%20them.%20%E2%80%9CSee%3F%20First%20I%20thought%20I%E2%80%99d%20distribute%20these%20only%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Balabhadra%20babu%E2%80%99s%20muffled%20voice%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20then%20I%20thought%20it%20is%20not%20the%20current%20picture.%20We%20should%20have%20an%20updated%20picture%20for%20this%20historic%20occasion%2C%20so%20lot%20of%20printing%20work%20also.%20Then%20I%20have%20to%20make%20banners%2C%20flags%2C%20headbands%2C%20everything.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20the%20programme%2C%20Bulbhaddar%20chacha%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalabhadra%20babu%20took%20off%20the%20mask.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20everyone%20can%E2%80%99t%20go%20for%20the%20temple%20consecration%20ceremony%20in%20Ayodhya.%20There%20is%20only%20limited%20capacity%2C%20no%3F%20But%20every%20Indian%E2%80%99s%20heart%20is%20filled%20with%20emotion%20and%20pride.%20Everyone%20wants%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20this%20sacred%20ceremony.%20So%20we%20are%20having%20ceremonies%20in%20every%20mohalla%20across%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCommunal%20prayer%3F%20Like%20the%20namaz%2C%20where%20everyone%20prays%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Tara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20like%20namaz%2C%20Madam.%20Our%20own%20ceremony.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBulbhaddar%20chacha%2C%20you%20will%20again%20order%20that%20non-veg%20cannot%20be%20sold%3F%20First%20that%20Rana%20took%20away%20all%20my%20supply%20and%20I%20had%20to%20remain%20closed.%20Just%20this%20morning%2C%20I%20have%20reopened%20and%20now%20again%20Kanwal%20and%20Nirmal%20will%20come%20and%20say%20%E2%80%98close%20down%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20put%20jhandis%20outside%20my%20shop.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArre%2C%20Laadley%2C%20why%20so%20much%20non-cooperation%20and%20negativity%3F%20You%20can%E2%80%99t%20stop%20selling%20meat%20for%20a%20few%20days%20to%20respect%20people%E2%80%99s%20sensibilities%3F%20We%20show%20tolerance%20or%20not%3F%20I%20have%20so%20many%20Muslim%20friends.%20During%20Ramzan%2C%20my%20wife%20used%20to%20complain%3A%20%E2%80%98Every%20day%20you%20have%20to%20go%20for%20an%20iftaar%20party%3F%E2%80%99%20My%20most%20senior%20shop%20attendant%20was%20Muslim.%20I%20always%20used%20to%20make%20sure%20he%20was%20free%20at%20namaz%20time%20%E2%80%93%20no%20matter%20what%20was%20going%20on%20in%20the%20shop%2C%20I%20would%20say%20to%20him%2C%20%E2%80%98You%20go%20to%20the%20mosque%20and%20finish%20your%20namaz%20first.%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamal%20had%20begun%20to%20titter%2C%20%E2%80%9CBulbhaddar%20chacha%2C%20now%20you%20are%20sounding%20like%20a%20fake%20secular%20who%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20actually%20know%20any%20Muslims%20at%20all.%20Otherwise%2C%20how%20many%20shop%20attendants%20do%20you%20know%20in%20the%20old%20city%20who%20take%20time%20off%20for%20namaz%3F%20Laadley%2C%20do%20you%20also%20send%20your%20man%20to%20first%20read%20his%20namaz%20when%20he%20is%20trying%20to%20light%20the%20tandoor%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20in%20the%20checked%20lungi%20and%20brown%20sweater%20laughed%20most%20heartily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EACP%20saheb%20was%20tired%2C%20but%20Constable%20Rana%20was%20completely%20exhausted.%20He%20had%20been%20up%20the%20previous%20night%2C%20then%20in%20the%20field%20all%20morning%2C%20and%20now%20he%20had%20been%20slapping%20Salman%20intermittently%20for%20the%20last%20one%20hour%20trying%20to%20get%20him%20to%20confess%20to%20the%20murder%20of%20Rahman%20miyan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20treated%20me%20badly%20but%20I%20never%20harmed%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20wailed%20Salman.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20threw%20me%20out%20again%20that%20evening%2C%20so%20I%20went%20and%20had%20a%20drink.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20many%20drinks%20did%20you%20have%3F%E2%80%9D%20Rana%20shook%20him%20violently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20few.%20I%20cry%20when%20I%20drink.%20I%20went%20back%20to%20plead%20with%20Rahman%20miyan%20privately%2C%20because%20I%20knew%20Arshad%20bhai%20would%20have%20left%20by%20then.%20But%20he%20was%20lying%20on%20the%20ground.%20I%20thought%20he%20was%20sleeping%3B%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20think.%20I%20took%20his%20folder%20from%20the%20table%20and%20went%20into%20the%20kitchen%20to%20see%20what%20was%20there.%20There%20was%20a%20full%20pateela%20of%20qorma%3B%20I%20thought%20I%E2%80%99ll%20take%20it%20and%20share%20it%20with%20everyone.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20ACP%20saheb%20tired%20of%20listening%20to%20the%20screams%2C%20he%20called%20for%20ASI%20Achche%20Lal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSir%2C%20I%20think%20he%20was%20just%20at%20the%20wrong%20place%20at%20the%20wrong%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Achche%20Lal.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20drunk%2C%20went%20back%20to%20argue%2C%20or%20plead%2C%20saw%20that%20Rahman%20miyan%20was%20lying%20on%20the%20floor%20and%20took%20the%20opportunity%20to%20steal.%20Maybe%20he%20knew%20he%20was%20already%20dead%2C%20or%20maybe%20he%20really%20thought%20he%20was%20sleeping.%20God%20only%20knows!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20thought%20Rahman%20was%20sleeping%20on%20the%20floor%20with%20the%20whole%20place%20turned%20upside%20down%20around%20him%3F%20How%20do%20you%20know%20he%20isn%E2%80%99t%20lying%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAchche%20Lal%20shrugged%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20humble%20experience%2C%20sir.%20He%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20lasted%20so%20long%20in%20interrogation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20did%20he%20steal%20the%20documents%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20use%20for%20the%20NRC%20it%20seems.%20He%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20his%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20Achche%20Lal%20twirled%20the%20fingers%20of%20his%20right%20hand%20in%20a%20gesture%20that%20indicated%20bewilderment%20at%20Salman%E2%80%99s%20naivet%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20is%20an%20idiot%2C%20or%20what%3F%20Anyway%2C%20Achche%20Lal%2C%20I%20will%20be%20frank%20with%20you.%20I%20have%20felt%20from%20the%20beginning%20that%20the%20investigation%20has%20been%20deficient.%20You%20found%20out%20that%20Salman%20had%20brought%20the%20pateela%20to%20the%20madarsa%20but%20instead%20of%20arresting%20him%20there%20and%20then%2C%20you%20sat%20on%20the%20information.%20And%20another%20thing%2C%20you%20said%20take%20these%20people%20along%20%E2%80%93%20let%20them%20see%20when%20we%20interrogate%20Shambhu%2C%20but%20then%20nothing%20satisfies%20them.%20Now%20they%20are%20saying%20why%20did%20you%20arrest%20one%20and%20not%20the%20other!%20It%20is%20all%20part%20of%20an%20ecosystem.%20This%20communal%20card%20will%20come%20up%20again%2C%20just%20watch.%20Once%20you%20get%20used%20to%20playing%20the%20victim%20card%2C%20then%20you%20see%20everything%20through%20jaundiced%20eyes%2C%20no%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstable%20Rana%20knocked%20at%20the%20door%2C%20came%20in%20and%20smartly%20saluted.%20%E2%80%9CSir%2C%20he%20stole%20from%20there%3B%20that%20much%20is%20definite.%20But%20more%20than%20that%20he%20is%20not%20saying.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKeep%20him%20%E2%80%93%20you%20have%2014%20days.%20Then%20let%20him%20go%20into%20judicial%20custody.%20When%20you%20file%20the%20chargesheet%20after%20three%20months%2C%20put%20Section%20302.%20If%20the%20new%20criminal%20Act%20is%20allowed%20to%20come%20in%20by%20then%2C%20he%20would%20be%20tried%20for%20stealing.%20But%20if%20it%20is%20the%20old%20Act%20still%2C%20he%20would%20be%20tried%20for%20murder.%20It%20will%20depend%20on%20his%20luck.%20And%20his%20lawyers%20and%20supporters%20will%20also%20learn%20that%20it%20is%20not%20good%20to%20oppose%20every%20single%20change.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EASI%20Achche%20Lal%20and%20Constable%20Rana%20looked%20at%20him%20uncertainly.%20The%20ACP%20burst%20out%20laughing%2C%20%E2%80%9CJoking%2C%20bhai%2C%20joking.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20be%20continued%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EShahrukh%20Alam%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20write%20a%20murder%20mystery%20for%20a%20very%20long%20time.%20She%20has%20written%20versions%20of%20this%20story%20since%202013%20and%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Wire%3Cem%3E%C2%A0has%20published%20one%20such%20version%20earlier.%20She%20is%20hopeful%20that%20she%E2%80%99ll%20deliver%20a%20complete%20mystery%20this%20time.%20%F0%9F%A4%9E%F0%9F%8F%BB%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705397169000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16145502%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-16-at-1.34.36-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffiction%2Fa-mood-for-murder-episode-8-with-spice%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Wire%20WhoDunnIt%3A%20This%20is%20the%20eighth%20part%20of%20a%20serialised%20detective%20story%20by%20Shahrukh%20Alam.%20It%20is%20a%20work%20of%20fiction.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffiction%2Fa-mood-for-murder-episode-8-with-spice%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IndiGo%2C%20Mumbai%20airport%20operator%20get%20notices%20after%20passengers%20eat%20on%20tarmac%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publishe