0detained%20for%20verification.%20On%20spot%20verification%2C%20they%20disclosed%20themselves%20as%20(a)%20Name%3A%20Philip%20khaikholal%20khongsai%2C%20son%20of%20(Late)%20Marcus%20Khongsai%20of%20New%20Moreh%20Ward%20no%208.%20(b)%20Hemkholal%20Mate%2C%20son%20of%20(Late)%20Onkholun%20Mate%20of%20K.%20Moulsang%20Village.%20The%20above%20two%20individuals%20were%20arrested.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuki-Zo%20women%20in%20Moreh%20have%20protested%20against%20the%20arrest%20and%20demanded%20the%20unconditional%20and%20immediate%20release%20of%20the%20two%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENyay%20Yatra%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20entered%20Kangpokpi%20on%20day%20two.%20Over%20thousands%20of%20people%20gathered%20on%20the%20streets%20from%20Gamgiphai%20via%20Kangpokpi%20town%20to%20Hengbung%20village%20to%20welcome%20Gandhi%20in%20the%20Kuki-majority%20district.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKangpokpi%20district%20is%20among%20the%20110%20in%2015%20states%2C%20which%20will%20be%20covered%20by%20the%20Yatra.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMembers%20of%20the%20Kuki%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Organisation%20for%20Human%20Rights%2C%20who%20walked%20along%20with%20the%20senior%20Congress%20leader%2C%20apprised%20him%20of%20the%20current%20situation%20in%20Manipur.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20told%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20that%20unless%20the%20state%20forces%2C%20especially%20the%20Meitei%20commandos%2C%20are%20withdrawn%2Fremoved%20from%20the%20border%20town%2C%20there%20will%20be%20no%20peace%20in%20Moreh%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Committee%20on%20Tribal%20Unity%20(COTU)%20and%20various%20civil%20society%20organisations%20of%20Kangpokpi%20also%20requested%20Gandhi%20to%20present%20the%20grievances%20of%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community%20in%20the%20upcoming%20budget%20session%20of%20parliament.%20Their%20leader%20Lun%20Kipgen%2C%20who%20spent%20about%2030%20minutes%20with%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Jairam%20Ramesh%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20these%20are%20the%20demands%20which%20they%20had%20raised%20with%20Gandhi%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3E%20A%20separate%20administration%20for%20Kuki-Zo%20people%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20Union%20Territory%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20central%20university%20for%20both%20Kangpokpi%20and%20Lamka%20in%20Churachandpur%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3E%20An%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20at%20Kangpokpi%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3E%20A%20Kuki-Zo%20Regiment%20in%20the%20military%2Fdefence%20sector%20for%20the%20post-conflict%20scenario%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Permanent%20HQ%20for%20Central%20Security%20Forces%2FAssam%20Rifles%20in%20Phailengmol%20areas%20in%20Saikul%2C%20Kangchup-Geljang%2C%20Imphal%20Tamenglong%20(IT)%20Road%2C%20Taphou%20Kuki%2C%20which%20are%20the%20boundaries%20between%20Kuki-Zo%20dominated%20areas%20and%20Non%20Kuki-Zo%20dominated%20areas%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Permanent%20removal%20of%20State%20Police%20Commandos%20(CDOs)%20from%20Moreh%2C%20and%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Express-highways%20between%20Kangpokpi%20to%20Lamka%20(Churachandpur)%20via%20Joujangtek%2C%20Kangpokpi%20to%20Tengnoupal-Moreh%20via%20Saikul-Phailengmol%20and%20Tengnoupal-Moreh%20Churachandpur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705388899000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16123414%2FScreenshot-2024-01-16-at-12.33.58%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-churachandpur-congress-moreh-nyay-yatra%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Members%20of%20the%20Kuki%20Women's%20Organisation%20for%20Human