happy%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20had%20%26quot%3Bmade%20them%20demanding%20and%20greedy.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''They%20have%20lost%20touch%20with%20where%20they've%20come%20from.%20They're%20rubbing%20people's%20noses%20in%20it%20by%20flashing%20their%20cash%2C%20which%20I%20think%20is%20downright%20nasty%2C''%20Ms%20Bayford%20added%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705386960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2Fubje8118_a-large-amount-of-her-lottery-will-go-toward-paying-for-her-house_625x300_04_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-cuts-ties-with-greedy-and-demanding-family-after-rs-1-550-crore-lottery-win-4871884%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22MsBayford%20said%20she%20severed%20ties%20with%20her%20family%20after%20they%20became%20too%20''greedy''%20and%20tried%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20her%20generosity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-cuts-ties-with-greedy-and-demanding-family-after-rs-1-550-crore-lottery-win-4871884%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Republic%20Day%20offer%3A%20Jio%20offers%20partner%20coupons%2C%20special%20benefits%2C%20and%20more%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705386882000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-08%2F21%2Ffull%2F1692584742-9572.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Frepublic-day-offer-jio-offers-partner-coupons-special-benefits-and-more-124011600256_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20coupons%20will%20become%20available%20in%20the%20user's%20MyJio%20account%20after%20recharging%20with%20the%20Rs%202%2C999%20Jio%20prepaid%20plan%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22ht