20Poverty%20Reduction%20Distort%20the%20Truth%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16105531%2Findia-585078_1280.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhile%20the%20NITI%20Aayog%20has%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.niti.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2024-01%2FMPI-22_NITI-Aayog20254.pdf%5C%22%3Enew%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%2024.8%20crore%20people%20have%20been%20lifted%20out%20of%20multidimensional%20poverty%20in%20the%20nine%20years%20leading%20up%20to%202022-23%2C%20experts%20of%20the%20economy%20have%20raised%20doubts%20over%20this%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20multidimensional%20measure%20looks%20at%20the%20areas%20covered%20in%20the%2012%20sustainable%20development%20goals%20across%20health%2C%20education%20and%20standard%20of%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMultidimensional%20poverty%20in%20India%20was%20found%20to%20decline%20from%2029.17%25%20in%202013-14%20to%2011.28%25%20in%202022-23%20with%20about%2024.82%20crore%20people%20escaping%20poverty%20during%20this%20period.%20At%20the%20States%E2%80%99%20level%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20topped%20the%20list%20with%205.94%20crore%20people%20escaping%20poverty%20followed%20by%20Bihar%20at%203.77%20crore%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20at%202.30%20crore%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20claims%20that%20some%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20initiatives%20%E2%80%93%20like%20Poshan%20Abhiyan%2C%20Anaemia%20Mukt%20Bharat%2C%20Ujjwala%20and%20others%20%E2%80%93%20have%20played%20%E2%80%9Ca%20crucial%20role%E2%80%9D%20in%20addressing%20different%20aspects%20of%20deprivation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20says%20that%20India%20is%20likely%20to%20achieve%20the%20SDG%20of%20%E2%80%9Chalving%20multidimensional%20poverty%E2%80%9D%20well%20before%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20tweeted%20about%20the%20government%20think-tank%E2%80%99s%20report%2C%20saying%2C%20%C2%A0%E2%80%9CVery%20encouraging%2C%20reflecting%20our%20commitment%20towards%20furthering%20inclusive%20growth%20and%20focusing%20on%20transformative%20changes%20to%20our%20economy.%20We%20will%20continue%20to%20work%20towards%20all-round%20development%20and%20to%20ensure%20a%20prosperous%20future%20for%20every%20Indian.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fniti-aayog-makes-huge-poverty-relief-claim-several-economists-raise-objections%2Fcid%2F1994004%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%2C%20experts%20have%20raised%20some%20serious%20doubts%20over%20the%20use%20of%20the%20Multidimensional%20Poverty%20Index%20(MPI)%20to%20make%20these%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20MPI%20simply%20tells%20us%20the%20percentage%20of%20people%20unable%20to%20access%20certain%20facilities%20provided%20by%20the%20government%20or%20(that%20are)%20available%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20retired%20Indian%20Economic%20Services%20officer%20K.L.%20Datta%20told%20the%20newspaper.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20used%20by%20planners%20and%20policymakers%20to%20fix%20targets%2C%20nor%20is%20it%20used%20as%20an%20input%20to%20make%20plans%20for%20poverty%20reduction.%20To%20sum%20up%2C%20the%20MPI%20does%20not%20represent%20poverty.%20The%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20project%20the%20MPI%20estimate%20as%20a%20substitute%20for%20the%20poverty%20ratio.%20This%20is%20not%20right.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEconomist%20Sunil%20Ray%2C%20former%20director%20of%20the%20A.N.%20Sinha%20Institute%2C%20Patna%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHow%20can%20a%20nation%20achieve%20SDG%20when%20its%20government%20has%20to%20ensure%20the%20survival%20of%20more%20than%20two-thirds%20of%20its%20population%20%5Bthrough%20the%20National%20Food%20Security%20Act%5D%3F%20The%20government%20is%20giving%20this%20freebie%20because%20the%20people%20are%20not%20self-dependent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEconomist%20and%20rights%20activist%20Jean%20Dr%C3%A8ze%20also%20expressed%20reservations%20about%20the%20use%20of%20the%20MPI.%20%E2%80%9C(The)%20MPI%20does%20not%20include%20any%20indicator%20of%20short-term%20purchasing%20power.%20Thus%2C%20we%20must%20read%20MPI%20data%20along%20with%20other%20information%2C%20including%20recent%20evidence%20of%20sluggish%20growth%20in%20real%20wages%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CMPI%20data%20can%20complement%20but%20not%20substitute%20for%20poverty%20estimates%20from%20consumer%20expenditure%20surveys%20that%20are%20long%20overdue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsis%20Banerjee%2C%20economist%20and%20former%20vice-chancellor%20of%20Calcutta%20University%2C%20added%20that%20while%20the%20MPI%20could%20not%20be%20used%20as%20a%20measure%20of%20poverty%2C%20this%20particular%20government%20also%20cannot%20take%20credit%20for%20a%20reduced%20MPI.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20(MPI)%20has%20been%20declining%20for%20quite%20some%20time%20now%20and%20not%20just%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years.%20Most%20studies%20show%20the%20credit%20for%20this%20goes%20to%20measures%20initiated%20before%20the%20change%20of%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20in%202014%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6there%20is%20the%20big%20mystery%20as%20to%20why%20there%20has%20been%20a%20slide%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20performance%20on%20the%20World%20Hunger%20Index%20in%20recent%20times%20if%20there%20has%20been%20such%20impressive%20reductions%20in%20poverty.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Findia-ranks-111th-among-125-countries-in-global-hunger-index-report%5C%22%3Ewas%20ranked%20111%20among%20125%20countries%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Global%20Hunger%20Index%20report%20released%20by%20two%20European%20agencies%20on%20October%2012%2C%202023.%20The%20only%20countries%20ranking%20lower%20than%20India%20were%20Timor-Leste%2C%20Mozambique%2C%20Afghanistan%2C%20Haiti%2C%20Guinea-Bissau%2C%20Liberia%2C%20Sierra%20Leone%2C%20Chad%2C%20Niger%2C%20Lesotho%2C%20Democratic%20Republic%20of%20Congo%2C%20Yemen%2C%20Madagascar%2C%20Central%20African%20Republic%2C%20South%20Sudan%2C%20Burundi%20and%20Somalia.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705382815000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16105531%2Findia-585078_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Feconomists-say-niti-aayog-claims-on-poverty-reduction-distort-the-truth%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20think-tank%20claimed%20that%2024.8%20people%20have%20been%20lifted%20out%20of%20multidimensional%20poverty%20in%20the%20nine%20years%20leading%20up%20to%202022-23%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Feconomists-say-niti-aayog-claims-on-poverty-reduction-distort-the-truth%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Emmys%20Succeeded%20Thanks%20to%20Delightful%20Nostalgia%2C%20Emotional%20Speeches%20and%20More%3A%20TV%20Review%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705382416000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FEmmys-Show-Review-Joan-Collins-and-Taraji-P-Henson.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235873319%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Four%20months%20late%20and%20coming%20off%20the%20heels%20of%20two%20strikes%2C%20an%20awkward%20Golden%20Globes%20and%20the%20Critics%20Choice%20Awards%2C%20there%20perhaps%20weren%E2%80%99t%20many%20expectations%20leading%20into%20the%2075th%20Primetime%20Emmys.%20When%20actor%20Anthony%20Anderson%20was%20announced%20as%20the%20host%2C%20it%20seemed%20like%20a%20safe%20albeit%20humdrum%20choice%20%E2%80%94%20until%20news%20of%20past%20sexual%20assault%20%5B%E2%80%