nd%20suggesting%20that%20a%20similar%20fate%20awaits%20in%20India.%20As%20one%20scrolls%20down%20the%20group%2C%20a%20viral%20image%20featuring%20Israeli%20President%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20directly%20addressing%20Hindus%2C%20claims%20that%20if%20Hindus%20are%20divided%20by%20caste%2C%20they%20will%20be%20erased.%20The%20image%20suggests%20that%20Israel%2C%20with%20its%2070%20lakh%20yahudis%20(Jews)%2C%20is%20more%20powerful%20than%2055%20Muslim%20countries%2C%20while%20in%20India%2C%20with%20100%20crore%20Hindu%20individuals%2C%20Hindus%20are%20portrayed%20as%20vulnerable%20and%20hunted%20in%20their%20own%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20messages%20appear%20to%20be%20more%20extreme%20than%20the%20narratives%20circulating%20on%20Facebook%20and%20Twitter%2C%20because%20WhatsApp%20allows%20the%20sharing%20of%20videos%20depicting%20graphic%20violence%20without%20any%20significant%20repercussions.%20In%20contrast%2C%20social%20media%20accounts%20could%20be%20banned%20on%20Facebook%20and%20X%2C%20in%20such%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20web%20of%20misinformation%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20depicting%20a%20decapitated%20body%20is%20circulating%20with%20a%20caption%20in%20Hindi%2C%20saying%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20Hamas%20which%20is%20being%20supported%20by%20the%20Congress%20and%20regional%20parties.%20So%2C%20think%20about%20what%20you%20have%20to%20do.%20Consider%20the%20fate%20of%20your%20country%2C%20your%20children%2C%20your%20tomorrow.%20You%20yourself%20are%20wise.%20Look%20at%20the%20actions%20of%20Hamas%20scoundrels%20with%20open%20eyes%20and%20consider%20those%20who%20support%20them.%20Keep%20in%20mind%20that%20those%20backing%20these%20individuals%20today%20are%20the%20same%20individuals%20working%20to%20convert%20India%20into%20an%20Islamic%20country.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20avoid%20seeing%20an%20Islamic%20State%20or%20Ghazwatul%20Hind%20in%20India%2C%20I%20urge%20all%20of%20you%20to%20recognise%20that%20the%20viral%20video%20alone%20won%E2%80%99t%20bring%20about%20change.%20Every%20Hindu%20must%20strive%20to%20prevent%20the%20Congress%20or%20any%20other%20opposition%20party%20from%20forming%20the%20government%20in%20India%20under%20any%20circumstances.%20Failure%20to%20do%20so%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20painful%20future%20for%20all%20of%20us%20and%20our%20families.%20Every%20Hindu%20should%20make%20every%20effort%20to%20support%20Modi%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%3Cem%3EJai%20Hind%2C%20Jai%20Bharat%2C%20Vande%20Mataram.%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20attack%20is%20being%20exploited%20on%20a%20large%20scale%20to%20instil%20fear%20among%20Indians%2C%20particularly%20Hindus%2C%20by%20suggesting%20that%20something%20even%20more%20ominous%20than%20the%20events%20in%20Israel%20will%20soon%20transpire%20in%20India.%20These%20messages%2C%20which%20have%20gone%20viral%20on%20WhatsApp%2C%20Facebook%20groups%2C%20and%20Twitter%2C%20spread%20misinformation%20in%20the%20form%20of%20videos%2C%20images%2C%20and%20text.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20specific%20message%2C%20widely%20circulated%20and%20forwarded%20numerous%20times%20on%20WhatsApp%2C%20has%20gained%20traction%20on%20Twitter%2C%20especially%20in%20Hindi.%20This%20message%20contains%20an%20image%20asserting%20that%20the%20removal%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20from%20power%20will%20lead%20to%20a%20genocide%20of%20Hindus.%20The%20claim%20is%20being%20linked%20to%20%E2%80%9Ca%20respected%20American%20journalist%2C%20Janet%20Levy%E2%80%9D.%20Upon%20looking%20for%20the%20mentioned%20article%20and%20person%2C%20Levy%2C%20I%20discovered%20that%20this%20Hindi%20piece%20refers%20to%20an%20old%20article%20published%20in%202015%20on%20a%20propaganda%20portal%20called%20%3Cem%3EAmerican%20Thinker%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20piece%20is%20titled%20%E2%80%98The%20Muslim%20Takeover%20of%20West%20Bengal.%E2%80%99%20The%20article%20was%20tweeted%20by%20former%20governor%20of%20West%20Bengal%20Tathagata%20Roy%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16081459%2FScreenshot-2024-01-16-at-8.14.37%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22882%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16081459%2FScreenshot-2024-01-16-at-8.14.37%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%20882w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16081459%2FScreenshot-2024-01-16-at-8.14.37%25E2%2580%25AFAM-255x300.png%20255w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16081459%2FScreenshot-2024-01-16-at-8.14.37%25E2%2580%25AFAM-872x1024.png%20872w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16081459%2FScreenshot-2024-01-16-at-8.14.37%25E2%2580%25AFAM-425x500.png%20425w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693125%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221036%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20particular%20tweet%20mentioned%20above%20has%20been%20shared%20by%20a%20verified%20Twitter%20handle.%20It%20was%20retweeted%20over%20300%20times%20and%20liked%20over%20400%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E%E0%A4%87%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%B2%20%E0%A4%AF%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%A7%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%9C%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%9F%20%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%B5%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%96%20%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%95%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%89%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%AF%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%97%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%9F%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%9F%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%80%20%