E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20situation%20is%20truly%20unfortunate.%20The%20propagation%20of%20anti-Muslim%20propaganda%20and%20disinformation%20by%20ordinary%20Indians%20poses%20not%20only%20a%20threat%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20social%20cohesion%2C%20but%20also%20jeopardises%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20policy%20interests.%20India%20has%20endeavoured%20to%20portray%20itself%20as%20a%20neutral%20entity%20in%20the%20Gaza%20war%2C%20advocating%20for%20humanitarian%20aid%20to%20Gaza.%20Just%20days%20ago%2C%20India%20voted%20at%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20in%20support%20of%20recognising%20the%20right%20of%20Palestinians%20to%20self-determination.%20Maintaining%20amicable%20relations%20with%20the%20Arab%20world%20is%20crucial%20for%20India%2C%20both%20for%20strategic%20and%20economic%20reasons%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20foreign%20policy%20expert%20Mohammad%20Zeeshan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20the%20spread%20of%20misinformation%20against%20Muslims%20constitutes%20a%20direct%20threat%20to%20these%20foreign%20policy%20interests%20and%20positions.%20Regrettably%2C%20global%20media%20has%20already%20taken%20notice%20of%20this%20issue.%20Since%20the%20October%207%20Hamas%20attacks%2C%20numerous%20reports%20in%20the%20international%20media%20have%20highlighted%20how%20misinformation%20against%20Muslims%20and%20Palestinians%20can%20be%20traced%20back%20to%20Indian%20accounts.%20This%20poses%20a%20direct%20challenge%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20goodwill%20and%20interests%20in%20the%20Arab%20world%20and%20on%20the%20global%20stage%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20spreading%20fake%20narratives%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20conflict%2C%20what%20stood%20out%20to%20me%20was%20the%20surprising%20prevalence%20of%20viral%20content%20on%20WhatsApp%20originating%20from%20ordinary%20people%2C%20rather%20than%20politically%20active%20users.%20These%20individuals%20aren%E2%80%99t%20explicitly%20aligned%20with%20any%20political%20party%3B%20they%20are%20regular%20villagers%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Kiran%20Garimella%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20at%20Rutgers%20School%20of%20Information%20and%20Communication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGarimella%20further%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAdditionally%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20an%20apparent%20effort%20to%20fuel%20anti-Muslim%20sentiments.%20The%20narrative%20implies%20that%20actions%20attributed%20to%20Hamas%20could%20also%20be%20carried%20out%20by%20Muslim%20neighbours%2C%20aligning%20with%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20political%20agenda.%20What%E2%80%99s%20particularly%20surprising%20is%20the%20consistent%20influx%20of%20content%20almost%20daily.%20These%20narratives%2C%20often%20originating%20from%20the%20Israeli%20side%2C%20are%20extensively%20propagated%20on%20WhatsApp.%20The%20nature%20of%20some%20content%2C%20such%20as%20claims%20about%20Hamas%20using%20child%20actors%2C%20raises%20questions%20about%20why%20Indian%20villagers%20would%20be%20invested%20in%20issues%20happening%20in%20distant%20regions%20where%20they%20have%20no%20apparent%20stake.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20a%20broader%20perspective%2C%20this%20phenomenon%20highlights%20the%20potential%20for%20an%20invested%20actor%2C%20equipped%20with%20the%20right%20infrastructure%2C%20to%20significantly%20amplify%20the%20spread%20of%20diverse%20content.%20This%20supercharging%20of%20infrastructure%20enables%20the%20widespread%20dissemination%20of%20specific%20narratives%2C%20showcasing%20the%20unexpected%20ways%20in%20which%20misinformation%20can%20be%20strategically%20utilised.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20observed%20over%2050%20narratives%20related%20to%20Israel%20and%20Palestine%20spreading%20in%20the%20groups%20we%20are%20monitoring%2C%20which%20is%20truly%20surprising.%20This%20possibly%20indicates%20a%20top-down%20content%20push%20by%20an%20invested%20actor.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20it%20is%20likely%20the%20BJP%2C%20attempting%20to%20demonstrate%20strong%20support%20for%20Israel.%20The%20Modi%20government%20has%20openly%20shown%20support%20for%20Israel%2C%20so%20part%20of%20it%20may%20be%20expressing%20solidarity%20with%20the%20Israeli%20side%20and%2C%20secondly%2C%20using%20this%20as%20a%20tool%20to%20fuel%20anti-Muslim%20sentiments.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20global%20menace%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20giants%20like%20Meta%20and%20X%20have%20already%20removed%20thousands%20of%20misleading%20posts%20following%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20Israel%20and%20its%20brutal%20attack%20on%20Gaza.%20However%2C%20experts%20say%20the%20volume%20of%20disinformation%20on%20the%20platforms%20regarding%20the%20war%2C%20especially%20in%20languages%20other%20than%20English%2C%20is%20dire.%20Even%20developed%20countries%20like%20the%20US%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20and%20several%20European%20nations%20are%20also%20recording%20a%20surge%20in%20anti-Muslim%20rhetoric%20following%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20with%20more%20than%20200%20million%20users%2C%20stands%20as%20WhatsApp%E2%80%99s%20largest%20market.%20Despite%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20impressive%20one%20billion%20phone%20subscribers%20with%20access%20to%20affordable%20data%2C%20it%20grapples%20with%20the%20rampant%20spread%20of%20fake%20news.%20Unlike%20X%20and%20Facebook%2C%20which%20have%20faced%20legislation%20addressing%20fake%20news%20and%20implemented%20corrective%20measures%20in%20various%20cases%2C%20WhatsApp%20has%20been%20somewhat%20lackadaisical%20in%20cracking%20down%20on%20unverified%20messages.%20The%20messaging%20platform%20has%20refrained%20from%20a%20proactive%20approach%20to%20address%20privacy%20concerns%20for%20its%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhatsApp%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Ftech%2Ftechnology%2Fwhatsapp-rolls-out-campaign-to-raise-user-safety-awareness-fight-misinformation%2Farticleshow%2F105387470.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Erevealed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%2090%25%20of%20fake%20news%20spreads%20through%20messages%20between%20two%20people.%20In%20response%20to%20this%20finding%2C%20WhatsApp%20is%20intensifying%20its%20education%20efforts%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20safety%20features%20and%20methods%20to%20identify%20fake%20news.%20The%20company%20issued%20a%20statement%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%202023%20outlining%20its%20commitment%20to%20this%20initiative.%20However%2C%20the%20platform%20clarified%20that%20it%20has%20no%20plans%20to%20alter%20its%20encrypted%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705373901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F25092830%2FWhatsapp_mmmm.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fwhatsapp-israel-gaza-anti-muslim%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hate%20messages%20have%20mostly%20gone%20viral%20in%20the%20Hindi%20belt%20where%20the%20saffron%20party%20has%20a%20vocal%20support%20base.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fwhatsapp-israel-gaza-anti-muslim%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Iran%20launches%20strikes%20on%20Israel's%20'spy%20headquarters'%20in%20Iraq%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705372921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106881402%2Cimgsize-68548.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Firan-launches-strikes-on-israels-spy-headquarters-in-iraq%2Farticleshow%2F106881346.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106881346.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIran's%20Revolutionary%20Guards%20have%20launched%20attacks%20in%20Iraq's%20Kurdistan%20region%20and%20Syria%2C%20targeting%20an%20alleged%20Israeli%20%26quot%3Bspy%20he